%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsabelle%20Fuhrman%20as%20Esther%20in%20the%20trailer%20for%20the%202009%20movie%20%26quot%3BOrphan.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20eventually%20discovers%20that%20she%20isn't%20Esther%20%E2%80%94%20in%20fact%2C%20she's%20a%2033-year-old%20woman%20called%20Leena%20Klammer%20with%20a%20pituitary%20condition%20responsible%20for%20her%20small%20stature.%20While%20she%20had%20previously%20been%20contained%20at%20an%20Estonian%20mental%20hospital%2C%20she's%20a%20serial%20killer%20who%20poses%20as%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20bloody%20confrontation%2C%20Leena%20is%20killed%20by%20her%20adoptive%20mother%20in%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3BOrphan%26quot%3B%20is%20obviously%20dramatized%2C%20it's%20widely%20believed%20that%20the%20inspiration%20Esther's%20character%20came%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fwoman-33-was-disguised-as-teen-boy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20bizarre%20case%20of%20Barbora%20%C5%A0krlov%C3%A1%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cspan%3E%C5%A0krlov%C3%A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20a%20Czech%20woman%20in%20her%2030s%20with%20%3Cspan%3Ehypopituitarism%2C%20was%20accused%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3ECzech%20%3Cspan%3Eauthorities%20of%20using%20the%20diminutive%20stature%20caused%20by%20her%20condition%20to%20pose%20as%20a%2013-year-old%20orphan%20girl.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPassing%20as%20a%20child%2C%20she%20was%20adopted%20by%20a%20woman%20named%20Klara%20Mauerova%2C%20who%20was%20later%20accused%20of%20abusing%20her%20two%20biological%20sons%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%C5%A0krlov%C3%A1%20was%20in%20her%20care.%20Later%2C%20in%20order%20to%20evade%20Czech%20authorities%20and%20avoid%20testifying%20in%20Mauerova's%20child-abuse%20case%2C%20%C5%A0krlov%C3%A1%2C%20then%2033%2C%20escaped%20to%20Norway%20and%20posed%20as%20a%2013-year-old%20boy%20named%20Adam.%20She%20was%20ultimately%20captured%20by%20aut