0(MTHL)%20has%20six%20lanes%2C%20and%2016.5%20km%20of%20the%20bridge's%20length%20is%20over%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%2C%20apart%20from%20bringing%20Mumbai%20and%20Navi%20Mumbai%20closer%2C%20the%20Atal%20Setu%20-%20named%20after%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20-%20will%20not%20only%20help%20ease%20traffic%20and%20enhance%20transportation%20but%20also%20serve%20as%20an%20engine%20of%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MTHL%20will%20provide%20faster%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20and%20the%20Navi%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20and%20also%20reduce%20travel%20time%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Pune%2C%20Goa%20and%20South%20India.%20It%20will%20also%20boost%20connectivity%20between%20the%20Mumbai%20Port%20and%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20Port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarthquake%20Resistant%2C%20Open%20Tolling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Atal%20Setu%20is%20India's%20first%20sea%20bridge%20to%20implement%20an%20open%20road%20tolling%20system%2C%20which%20will%20allow%20vehicles%20to%20pass%20through%20toll%20booths%20at%20speeds%20of%20up%20to%20100%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20without%20having%20to%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIT%20Bombay%20had%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Atal%20Setu%20during%20its%20construction%20in%202018%20and%20a%20team%20worked%20to%20ensure%20the%20design%20was%20done%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20falls%20under%20a%20moderate%20earthquake%20damage%20risk%20zone.%20Professor%20Deepankar%20Choudhury%2C%20Head%20of%20Civil%20Engineering%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20said%20that%20the%20bridge%20is%20built%20to%20withstand%20four%20different%20types%20of%20earthquakes%20of%20up%20to%206.5%20magnitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20the%20lights%20used%20on%20the%20bridge%20were%20also%20chosen%20carefully%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20do%20not%20disturb%20the%20aquatic%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20India's%20longest%20bridge%20built%20on%20the%20sea.%20Several%20technologies%20have%20been%20used%20in%20the%20making%20of%20this%20bridge%2C%20which%20are%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20The%20lights%20used%20in%20this%20bridge%20do%20not%20disturb%20the%20aquatic%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Commissioner%20of%20Mumbai%20Metropolitan%20Region%20Development%20Authority%20Dr%20Sanjay%20Mukherjee%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705056420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8hh9r9g8_atal-setu-ani_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-inaugurates-mumbai-trans-harbour-link-indias-longest-sea-bridge-4848937%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adding%20a%2021.8-km%20feather%20to%20the%20country's%20infrastructure%20cap%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20Mumbai%20Trans%20Harbour%20Link%20between%20Sewri%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Nhava%20Sheva%20in%20Raigad%20district%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-inaugurates-mumbai-trans-harbour-link-indias-longest-sea-bridge-4848937%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-inaugurates-mumbai-trans-harbour-link-indias-longest-sea-bridge-4848937%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-inaugurates-mumbai-trans-harbour-link-indias-longest-sea-bridge-4848937%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Does%20the%20CAG%20Live%20Up%20to%20the%20NDA's%20Election%20Promise%20of%20a%20Clean%20Government%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06163312%2FCAG-building-II.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9