st%20Israel%20has%20immense%20cultural%2C%20diplomatic%2C%20historical%2C%20and%20political%20significance.%20Israel%20has%20rejected%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20claim%20and%20vowed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67866342%5C%22%3Econtest%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20court%20cases%20such%20as%20these%20typically%20run%20for%20many%20years%20before%20a%20final%20judgement%20is%20reached%2C%20however%20South%20Africa%20has%20also%20requested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fcase%2F192%2Fpress-releases%5C%22%3Eprovisional%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20form%20of%20international%20injunction%20%E2%80%93%20and%20preliminary%20hearings%20will%20take%20place%20in%20The%20Hague%20on%20January%2011%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decision%20on%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20provisional%20measures%20request%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20made%20by%20the%20end%20of%20January%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20have%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20laws%20are%20in%20question%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fgenocideprevention%2Fdocuments%2Fatrocity-crimes%2FDoc.1_Convention%2520on%2520the%2520Prevention%2520and%2520Punishment%2520of%2520the%2520Crime%2520of%2520Genocide.pdf%5C%22%3E1948%20Convention%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Prevention%20and%20Punishment%20of%20the%20Crime%20of%20Genocide%20(Genocide%20Convention)%20was%20adopted%20following%20the%201940s%20holocaust%20by%20the%20Nazi%20regime%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20six%20million%20Jewish%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Genocide%20Convention%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20responses%20by%20the%20then%20fledgling%20United%20Nations%20to%20the%20holocaust.%20It%20was%20intended%20to%20clearly%20define%20genocide%2C%20prevent%20future%20genocides%2C%20and%20make%20nation%20states%20accountable%20for%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%20153%20parties%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20including%20Israel%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20it%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20pillars%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20human%20rights%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20are%20accountable%20for%20genocide%20before%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20while%20individuals%20can%20be%20charged%20with%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%20and%20placed%20on%20trial%20at%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenocide%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Finstruments-mechanisms%2Finstruments%2Fconvention-prevention-and-punishment-crime-genocide%5C%22%3Edefined%20in%20the%20Convention%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9Cacts%20committed%20with%20intent%20to%20destroy%2C%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%2C%20a%20national%2C%20ethnical%2C%20racial%20or%20religious%20group%E2%80%9D%20and%20extends%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Ekilling%20members%20of%20the%20group%2C%20or%20causing%20serious%20bodily%20harm%20to%20members%20of%20the%20group%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Edeliberately%20inflicting%20on%20the%20group%20conditions%20of%20life%20calculated%20to%20bring%20about%20its%20physical%20destruction%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eimposing%20measures%20to%20prevent%20births.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Israel%20under%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20was%20commenced%20on%20December%2029%2C%202023%20following%20lodgement%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcase-related%2F192%2F192-20231228-app-01-00-en.pdf%5C%22%3E84-page%20application%3C%2Fa%3E%20instituting%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20brought%20the%20case%20by%20relying%20on%20the%20principle%20that%20as%20a%20party%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20it%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20enforce%20legal%20rights%20owed%20to%20all%20people%20that%20genocide%20not%20be%20allowed.%20The%20claim%20could%20have%20been%20commenced%20by%20any%20other%20party%20to%20the%20convention%2C%20however%2C%20South%20Africa%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dirco.gov.za%2Fsouth-africa-calls-for-the-international-community-to-hold-israel-accountable-for-breaches-of-international-law%2F%5C%22%3Eraising%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20genocide%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20gives%20a%20historical%20context%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%20Palestine%2C%20recounts%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20details%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20Gaza%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticular%20attention%20is%20given%20to%20the%20actions%20and%20conduct%20of%20Israeli%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%2C%20especially%20their%20statements%20as%20to%20how%20Israel%20intended%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20and%20the%20extent%20and%20scale%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20and%20military%20objectives%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20then%20details%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actual%20military%20conduct%20during%20the%20Gaza%20campaign%20and%20the%20consequences%20for%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20This%20conduct%20is%20linked%20directly%20back%20to%20acts%20of%20genocide%20as%20defined%20in%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20court%20case%20takes%20two%20forms%3A%20a%20claim%20that%20Israel%20has%20committed%20genocide%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20urgent%20request%20for%20provisional%20measures%20(international%20legal%20speak%20for%20expediting%20the%20process).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20has%20requested%20that%20the%20court%20order%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%2C%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%2C%20immediately%20cease%20any%20activities%20that%20amount%20to%20an%20ongoing%20campaign%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20will%20need%20to%20prove%2C%20both%20in%20law%20and%20in%20facts%2C%20that%20the%20case%20is%20admissible%2C%20that%20the%20World%20Court%20has%20jurisdiction%20to%20hear%20this%20claim%2C%20and%20that%20the%20application%20is%20urgent%2C%20requiring%20orders%20to%20prevent%20irreparable%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20South%20Africa%20does%20not%20need%20to%20conclusively%20prove%20genocide%20has%20taken%20place.%20That%20comes%20at%20the%20later%20phase%2C%20called%20the%20Merits%20phase.%20South%20Africa%20does%2C%20however%2C%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20Palestinians%20face%20irreparable%20harm%20and%20that%2C%20on%20the%20facts%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20could%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20acts%20of%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20will%20no%20doubt%20robustly%20resist%20any%20assertion%20genocide%20is%20occurring%20and%20argue%20its%20political%20and%20military%20leaders%20are%20acting%20consistently%20with%20international%20law%20in%20response%20to%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20Hamas.%20Particular%20attention%20will%20probably%20be%20given%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20right%20of%20self-defence%20following%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20cases%20like%20these%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20has%20been%20thrust%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20being%20asked%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20settle%20that%20dispute.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20as%20a%20United%20Nations%20organ%2C%20is%20purely%20to%20apply%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20and%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20be%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20its%20role%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20face%20of%20claims%20of%20an%20ongoing%20genocide.%20This%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20how%20it%20has%20moved%20quickly%20to%20hear%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20potential%20outcomes%20from%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20provisional%20measures%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20may%20decline%20to%20order%20provisional%20measures.%20It%20may%2C%20for%20example%2C%20find%20it%20lacks%20jurisdiction%20and%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20inadmissible%20on%20technical%20legal%20grounds%2C%20or%20the%20facts%20do%20not%20support%20the%20claims%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20the%20court%20may%20uphold%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20request%20and%20order%20provisional%20measures.%20Any%20provisional%20measures%20ruling%20against%20Israel%20would%20require%20a%20radical%20modification%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cannot%2C%20however%2C%20enforce%20its%20decisions.%20In%202022%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Russia%20ignored%20an%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2022%2Fmar%2F16%2Fun-international-court-of-justice-orders-russia-to-halt-invasion-of-ukraine%5C%22%3Eprovisional%20measures%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20the%20court%20orders%2C%20Israel%20will%20retain%20its%20right%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jurist.org%2Fcommentary%2F2023%2F12%2F7-10-the-question-of-israels-right-to-self-defense-under-international-law%2F%5C%22%3Eself-defence%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Hamas.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%