signed%20with%20China%20focuses%20on%20tourism.%20Another%20agreement%20frontlines%20infrastructure.%20However%2C%20China%20has%20a%20checkered%20history%20of%20delivering%20on%20infrastructural%20promises%2C%20something%20the%20Maldives%20has%20to%20tolerate%20as%20a%20pawn%20in%20the%20Asian%20giant's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%20With%20the%20unequal%20relationship%20defined%20by%20escalating%20Chinese%20strategic%20interests%20in%20host%20nations%2C%20Maldives%20can%20look%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caspianpolicy.org%2Fresearch%2Fenergy-and-economy-program-eep%2Fthe-hidden-costs-of-kazakhstans-engagement-with-china-a-decade-of-the-belt-and-road%5C%22%3Eother%20central%20Asian%20partners%20of%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20how%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20BRI%20has%20progressed%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20high%20debt%20and%20low%20development.%20Nepal's%20foreign%20minister%20has%20said%20despite%20signing%20for%20the%20BRI%20in%202017%2C%20over%20six%20years%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fnational%2F2023%2F06%2F27%2Fnepal-yet-to-execute-bri-projects-says-foreign-minister-saud%5C%22%3Enot%20a%20single%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20mountain%20country%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20a%20candidate%20supported%20by%20jailed%20former%20Maldivian%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen%2C%20led%20the%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20in%20a%20reversal%20of%20former%20President%20Ibu%20Solih's%20%26quot%3BIndia%20First%26quot%3B%20policy.%20Unlike%20India's%20approach%20of%20development-led%20lending%20to%20partner%20nations%2C%20though%2C%20Chinese%20strategic%20investment%20allowed%20the%20economically%20mighty%20nation%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatvnews.com%2Fopinion%2Fnews-enter-the-dragon-chinese-entrenchment-proving-costly-for-maldives-abdulla-yameen-pro-chinese-ppm-pnc-coalition-752327%5C%22%3Elease%2017%20islands%3C%2Fa%3E%20prior%20to%20a%20controversial%20law%20enacted%20by%20Yameen's%20administration%20before%202019.%20The%20encroachment%20of%20land%20belonging%20to%20BRI%20partners%20by%20China%20is%20a%20tested%20method%2C%20and%20the%20expansionist%20power%20claims%20much%20land%20outside%20its%20own%20borders.%20In%202022%2C%20a%20leaked%20report%20with%20the%20Nepal%20government%20showed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-60288007%5C%22%3Esignificant%20encroachment%20on%20Nepali%20territory%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20China%2C%20But%20the%20debate%20lost%20its%20sheen%20quickly%20since%20the%20country's%20administration%20is%20indebted%20to%20its%20creditor%2C%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20Maldives%2C%20however%2C%20foreign%20interference%20could%20mean%20halted%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20and%20debt-trap%20%26quot%3Bdiplomacy%26quot%3B%20(the%20country%20owes%20close%20to%20%24%201.3%20billion)%2C%20and%20a%20major%20security%20threat%20to%20India%20even%20beyond%20China's%20String%20of%20Pearls%20agenda%20to%20encircle%20India%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region.%20The%20leased%20island%20of%20Feydhoo%20Finolhu%20provides%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20rapidly%20China%20can%20work%20at%20utilising%20its%20leases%20to%20threaten%20India.%20The%20island%2C%20leased%20by%20China%20till%202066%2C%20has%20grown%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20its%20original%20size%20to%20100%2C000%20square%20metres%2C%20less%20than%20700%20km%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20allying%20with%20China%2C%20the%20country%20has%20also%20remained%20the%20hub%20of%20radical%20Islamic%20terror%2C%20sending%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowyinstitute.org%2Fthe-interpreter%2Fmaldives-legacy-islamic-state%5C%22%3EIslamic%20State%20fighters%20per%20capita%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20any%20other%20nation.%20Some%20Maldivian%20survivors%20are%20held%20in%20camps%20in%20Syria%2C%20while%20the%20country%20takes%20in%20a%20massive%20population%20of%20foreign%20workers%2C%20often%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20which%20makes%20up%20close%20to%2020%25%20of%20its%20small%20population.%20The%20country%20is%20now%20host%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Fmaldives-now-hub-of-isis-pakistani-terror-groups-narco-networks-intel-sources-to-news18-8733797.html%5C%22%3Enarco-terror%20syndicates%20operated%20out%20of%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20terror-sponsoring%20partner%20to%20the%20Chinese%2C%20and%20these%20syndicates%20aid%20in%20promoting%20radical%20Islamic%20terror%20to%20young%20Maldivian%20men.%20Despite%20former%20home%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram's%20intervention%20in%202010%20to%20extract%20a%20promise%20to%20not%20host%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20operatives%2C%20Maldives%20has%20functioned%20as%20a%20base%20for%20terror%20operations.%20Intelligence%20shows%20that%20the%20radicalisation%20functions%20in%20concert%20with%20anti-India%20messaging%2C%20along%20with%20the%20drug%20and%20trafficking%20operations%2C%20all%20of%20which%20China%20is%20happy%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20tacitly%20support.%20It%20has%20operated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wionews.com%2Fworld%2Fis-china-trying-to-revive-a-terrorist-group-in-pakistan-occupied-kashmir-312371%5C%22%3Eto%20revive%20such%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmiri%20territory%20despite%20Chinese%20citizens%20being%20major%20victims%20of%20terrorism%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20economy%20exists%20in%20a%20fragile%20balance%20between%20tourism%2C%20agriculture%2C%20fisheries%20and%20Chinese%20debt.%20Amidst%20its%20row%20with%20India%20and%20President%20Muizzu%20opting%20for%20China%20as%20his%20first%20stop%2C%20the%20island%20nation%20wants%20Chinese%20tourists%20to%20make%20up%20for%20losses%20due%20to%20Indian%20cancellations.%20Indian%20tourists%20were%20the%20largest%20group%20of%20visitors%20in%202023%2C%20making%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fmaldives-row-indias-swift-response-former-maldivian-minister-warns-of-economic-suicide-11704886935956.html%5C%22%3E11%25%20of%20the%20country's%20tourism%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20China%20will%20be%20able%20to%20compensate%20in%20this%20department%2C%20considering%20its%20own%20slowing%20economy%20due%20to%20Covid%20lockdowns%20that%20are%20showing%20long-lasting%20effects.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20climate-endangered%20country%20had%20discussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1820208%5C%22%3Erenewable%20power%20transmission%20with%20India%20under%20the%20One%20Sun%2C%20One%20World%20and%20One%20Grid%20initiative%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20had%20offered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1847627%5C%22%3EUSD%20100%20million%20line%20of%20credit%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20former%20President%20Solih.%20The%20country's%20inorganic%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Out%26quot%3B%20platform%20that%20brought%20Muizzu%20to%20power%20will%20cause%20much%20of%20the%20promises%20to%20go%20unrealized%20unless%20the%20President%20is%20able%20to%20draw%20a%20clear%20balance%2C%20which%20seems%20more%20and%20more%20unlikely%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20despite%20Maldivian%20assurances%20that%20New%20Delhi%20remained%20a%20strategic%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20China%20hypocritically%20calls%20out%20%26quot%3Bexternal%20interference%26quot%3B%20in%20Maldives%2C%20it%20is%20significant%20that%20its%20anti-India%20messaging%20found%20root%20in%20a%20country%20where%20civil%20society%20had%20already%20been%20engaged%20with%20radicalization%2C%20and%20its%20youth%20embroiled%20in%20drug%20trade.%20It%20is%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20India-Maldives%20ties%20that%20there%20was%20no%20equal%20but%20positive%20messaging%20to%20counter%20any%20of%20the%20sentiments%2C%20and%20a%