handrayaan-3-scientist-basks-in-the-spotlight-capturing-hearts-fans-say-mohan-bhargav-hai-woh-watch%2Farticleshow%2F106764407.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Government%20Ends%20Honorarium%20to%20Madrasa%20Teachers%2C%20Move%20to%20Adversely%20Affect%201%20Million%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12152736%2FEffect-64.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucknow%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20stopped%20the%20honorarium%20of%20teachers%20hired%20to%20teach%20modern%20subjects%20in%20the%20madrasas%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20will%20adversely%20impact%20the%20livelihood%20of%20nearly%2021%2C000%20teachers%20and%20the%20education%20of%20nearly%20one%20million%20madrasa-going%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20decision%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20majoritarian%20politics%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20second%20major%20attack%20on%20minority%20education%20after%20withdrawing%20from%20the%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Fellowship%20in%202022.%20This%20decision%20has%20shocked%20thousands%20of%20teachers%20who%20have%20been%20persistently%20protesting%20for%20their%20honorarium%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20impart%20modern%20education%20to%20madrasa-going%20students%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20appointed%20over%2021%2C000%20teachers%20in%207%2C742%20madrasas%20in%20the%20state.%20These%20teachers%20were%20appointed%20under%20the%20prestigious%20SPQEM%20(Scheme%20for%20Providing%20Quality%20Education%20in%20Madrasas)%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20to%20modernise%20the%20education%20system%20in%20religious%20schools%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20Modi%20government%20came%20back%20to%20power%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20begun%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20this%20scheme.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20pro-Hindutva%20government%20slashed%20the%20budget%20of%20SPQEM%2C%20and%20later%20on%2C%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202017-18%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20stopped%20releasing%20funds%20for%20the%20modern%20education%20of%20madrasa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20union%2C%20teachers%20moved%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%2C%20organised%20protests%2C%20and%20met%20with%20the%20ministers%20concerned%20and%20administrative%20authorities%2C%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20didn%E2%80%99t%20release%20the%20funds.%20Teachers%20say%20that%20after%20their%20long%20fight%20for%20four%20years%2C%20they%20got%20an%20honorarium%20of%20only%2010%20months%20in%20the%20years%202021-22%2C%20which%20was%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdrop%20in%20the%20ocean%E2%80%9D%20because%20only%2025%25%20to%2030%25%20of%20madrasas%20received%20an%20honorarium%2C%20and%20other%20madrasas%20were%20denied%20it%20in%20the%20name%20of%20anomalies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F03161038%2Fimage_6483441-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221148%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F03161038%2Fimage_6483441-2.jpg%201148w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F03161038%2Fimage_6483441-2-300x132.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F03161038%2Fimage_6483441-2-1024x450.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-550256%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMadrasa%20teachers%20protesting%20in%20Lucknow.%20Photo%3A%20Asad%20Rizvi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20state%20government%20gave%20a%20little%20support%20to%20these%20teachers%20by%20giving%20them%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20for%20graduate%20and%20postgraduate%20teachers%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20an%20additional%20honorarium.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20current%20financial%20year%202023-24%2C%20teachers%20have%20not%20received%20this%20additional%20honorarium%20since%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENow%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20issued%20a%20fresh%20order%20to%20stop%20the%20additional%20honorarium%2C%20following%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20Union%20ministry%20of%20minority%20affairs%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20state%20government%20regarding%20this%20issue%20on%20October%2017%2C%202023.%20A%20letter%20apprised%20the%20state%20government%20that%20SPQEM%20was%20valid%20only%20until%20the%20financial%20year%202021-22%2C%20following%20which%20the%20government%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20stop%20additional%20honorarium%20on%20January%205%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20getting%20the%20order%20from%20the%20top%20bosses%2C%20the%20minority%20welfare%20department%20issued%20directions%20to%20all%20the%20district%20minority%20welfare%20officers%20on%20January%208%20this%20year%20to%20stop%20additional%20honorarium.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20SPQEM%20was%20introduced%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20in%202009.%20It%20was%20initially%20under%20the%20ministry%20of%20human%20resource%20development%20(HRD)%2C%20and%20on%20April%201%2C%202021%2C%20it%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20ministry%20of%20minority%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20funds%20for%20the%20honorarium%20came%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20funding%20arrangement%20changed%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202018-19%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20only%20paid%2060%25%20of%20the%20honorarium%20amount%2C%20with%20state%20governments%20responsible%20for%20arranging%20the%20remaining%2040%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20news%20that%20the%20state%20government%20also%20ended%20the%20additional%20honorarium%20stunned%20thousands%20of%20teachers%20because%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20they%20do%20not%20get%20any%20financial%20assistance%20from%20governments%20for%20their%20services.%20These%20teachers%20have%20been%20protesting%20for%20the%20release%20of%20their%20pending%20funds%20in%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20since%20International%20Minority%20Rights%20Day%20on%20December%2018%2C%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funion-govt-appointed-madrasa-teachers-in-up-havent-received-honorariums-in-4-years%5C%22%3EUnion%20Govt-Appointed%20Madrasa%20Teachers%20in%20UP%20Haven%E2%80%99t%20Received%20Honorariums%20in%204%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20latest%20order%20came%20as%20a%20setback%20to%20these%20thousands%20of%20teachers%20who%20teach%20subjects%20like%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20mathematics%2C%20science%2C%20social%20science%2C%20computers%2C%20etc.%2C%20in%20different%20madrasas%2C%20and%20they%20are%20perturbed%20about%20their%20livelihood.%20They%20feel%20that%20their%20years-long%20services%20are%20going%20in%20vain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%C2%A0However%2C%20teachers%20vow%20to%20continue%20their%20struggle%20for%20their%20pending%20payments.%20Ashraf%20Ali%2C%20alias%20Sikander%2C%20president%20of%20Madrasa%20Aadhunikaran%20Shikshak%20Ekta%20Samiti%2C%20says%20the%20state%20government%20wrecked%20the%20livelihood%20of%20teachers%20and%20will%20leave%20a%20million%20students%20deprived%20of%20modern%20education.%20According%20to%20Ali%2C%20teachers%20will%20continue%20their%20agitation%20until%20the%20government%20clears%20all%20their%20pending%20dues.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20also%20protest%20to%20mount%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%20for%20the%20renewal%20of%20our%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFrom%20time%20to%20time%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Madrasa%20Education%20Board%20has%20also%20pleaded%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20the%20release%20of%20honorariums%20for%20these%20teachers.%20When%20contacted%2C%20Iftekhar%20Ahmad%20Javed%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20board%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20January%2010%20and%20urged%20the%20renewal%20of%20SPQEM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%C2%A0In%20his%20letter%2C%20Javed%20reminisced%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%202018%20speech%2C%20in%20which%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20of%20India%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20empowering%20the%20Muslim%20youth.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20them%20to%20have%20the%20Quran%20in%20one%20hand%20and%20a%20computer%20in%20the%20other.%E2%80%9D%20Javed%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20appalling%2C%20as%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20honorarium%20could%20collapse%20the%20madrasa%20education%20system%2C%20where%20students%20from%20underprivileged%20households%20take%20admission%20for%20their%20primary%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Modi%20government%20does%20want%20to%20give%20funds%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%C2%A0This%20was%20not%20the%20first%20attempt%20by%20the%20saffron%20party%20government%20to%20target%20minority%20education.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20ended%20the%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Fellowship%20(MANF).%20This%20decision%20hampered%20the%20higher%20education%20of%20hundreds%20of%20students%20belonging%20to%20six%20notified%20minority%20communities%2C%20including%20Muslims%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Christians%2C%20Jains%2C%20Parsis%2C%20and%20Sikhs.%20Muslims%20were%20the%20main%20beneficiaries%20of%20MANF%2C%20who%20pursued%20courses%20like%20M.Phil.%20and%20Ph.D.%20with%20its%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%C2%A0It%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20in%202023%2C%20a%20report%20was%20prepared%20based%20on%20the%20analysis%20of%20data%20from%20the%20Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20Plus%20(UDISE%2B)%20and%20the%20All%20India%20Survey%20of%20Higher%20Education%20(AISHE)%2C%20which%20revealed%20that%20enrolment%20in%20higher%20education%20among%20Muslim%20students%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018%E2%80%9323%20dropped%20by%20more%20than%208.5%25%20in%202020%E2%80%932022.%20According%20to%20a%20report%2C%20while%2021%20lakh%20Muslim%20students%20had%20enrolled%20for%20higher%20education%20in%202019%E2%80%9320%2C%20the%20number%20fell%20to%2019.21%20lakh%20in%202020%E2%80%9321.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Vidhan%20Parishad%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%2C%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Madrasa%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20honorarium%20several%20times%20last%20year.%20Ashutosh%20Sinha%2C%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20MLC%2C%20says%20he%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20these%20teachers%20on%20the%20Floor%20of%20the%20House%2C%20and%20the%20government%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20contact%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20release%20their%20payment%20until%20March%202023.%20Sinha%20further%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20showing%20apathy%20as%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20madrasas%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20that%20there%20is%20no%20coordination%20between%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Muslim%20intellectuals%20see%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20following%20the%20playbook%20of%20its%20ideological%20parent%2C%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20disempower%20Muslims%20in%20India.%20Professor%20Nadeem%20Hasnain%20says%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20outreach%20programmes%20like%20Pasmanda%20and%20Sufi%20conferences%2C%20or%20Shukriya%20Modi%20Bhaijaan%2C%20are%20merely%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceyewash%E2%80%9D%3B%20they%20want%20to%20hamper%20their%20education%20to%20make%20them%20illiterate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHasnain%2C%20former%20head%20of%20the%20Anthropology%20department%20at%20Lucknow%20University%2C%20believes%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20differences%2C%20the%20madrasas%20are%20giving%20education%20to%20millions%20of%20students%20coming%20from%20economically%20weaker%20families.%20%E2%80%9CMadrasas%20have%20become%20an%20eyesore%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%2C%20and%20the%20government%20does%20not%20want%20to%20give%20them%20funds.%20When%20they%20collect%20donations%20from%20the%20community%2C%20agencies%20look%20at%20them%20with%20suspicion.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20since%20the%20Yogi%20government%20came%20into%20power%2C%20madrasas%20are%20persistently%20facing%20crackdowns%20in%20the%20name%20of%20surveys%20and%20investigations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705054507000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12152736%2FEffect-64.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fup-government-ends-honorarium-to-madrasa-teachers-move-to-adversely-affect-1-million-students%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government's%20decision%2C%20based%20on%20a%20Union%20government's%20order%2C%20will%20rob%20the%20livelihood%20of%20nearly%2021%2C000%20teachers%20who%20teach%20modern%20subjects%20in%207%2C742%20madrasas%20across%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fup-government-ends-honorarium-to-madrasa-teachers-move-to-adversely-affect-1-million-students%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20husband%20was%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20his%20career%20to%20be%20a%20stay-at-home%20parent%20but%20I%20wasn't.%20Here%20are%20the%20best%20and%20worst%20parts%20of%20our%20arrangement.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223413%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrea%20Mac%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20four%20children.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d90186979d7371821bf50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Mac%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndrea%20Mac%20is%20a%20growth%20strategist%20and%20her%20husband%20has%20been%20a%20stay-at-home%20dad%20for%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20couple%20has%20four%20kids%20ranging%20from%20age%205%20to%2019%20years%20old.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndrea%20said%20there's%20no%20clear%20guidance%20on%20how%20couples%20can%20navigate%20this%20arena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Andrea%20Mac%2C%20a%20growth%20strategist%20who%20started%20her%20own%20revenue%20and%20growth%20consultancy%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprequal.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EPrequal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20Greater%20Chicago%20area.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20four%20children%2C%20ages%2019%2C%2014%2C%207%2C%20and%205%20%E2%80%94%20and%20while%20I'm%20the%20family's%20breadwinner%2C%20my%20husband%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2