2Fbreadwinner-in-marriage-stay-at-home-dad-advice-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20breadwinner%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20my%20marriage%20while%20my%20husband%20is%20a%20stay-at-home%20dad%20has%20pros%20and%20cons.%20Here%20are%20five%20things%20about%20being%20a%20breadwinner%20that%20I'm%20most%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20It%20gives%20my%20husband%20more%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20least%20discussed%20factor%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20even%20the%20most%20unpopular%20to%20publicly%20state%20%E2%80%94%20is%20how%20my%20work%20opens%20up%20more%20doors%20for%20my%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20our%20family's%20day-to-day%20demands%20evolve%2C%20my%20role%20as%20the%20primary%20financial%20provider%20will%20eventually%20open%20up%20options%20for%20my%20husband.%20He's%20not%20boxed%20into%20traditional%20career%20paths%20or%20rigid%20timelines.%20Instead%2C%20he%20has%20the%20liberty%20to%20explore%20his%20passions%20and%20interests%20without%20the%20pressure%20of%20being%20the%20sole%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20he'll%20choose%20to%20pursue%20a%20dream%20job%2C%20experiment%20in%20new%20fields%2C%20volunteer%2C%20or%20not%20return%20to%20work%20at%20all.%20This%20flexibility%20feels%20like%20my%20most%20significant%20contribution%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbreadwinner-benefit-invisible-unpaid-labor-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20breadwinner%20and%20a%20great%20gift%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20I%20can%20give%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20I'm%20freed%20up%20from%20certain%20childcare%20demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20husband%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20at%20home%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20constantly%20adjust%20my%20day%20for%20unexpected%20child%20needs%20or%20unpaid%20work.%20When%20a%20sick%20kid%20needs%20to%20stay%20home%20or%20if%20one%20kid%20needs%20a%20last-minute%20costume%20for%20some%20school