eurs%20and%2021%20members%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Working%20Groups%20have%20warned%20that%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza%20reflects%20%E2%80%9Ca%20genocide%20in%20the%20making%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20overt%20intent%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdestroy%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20under%20occupation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntent%20from%20conduct%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20a%20genocidal%20intent%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20living%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20way%20in%20which%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20attack%20is%20being%20conducted%2C%20which%20has%20been%20described%20by%20Ms%20Hassim%20SC.%20It%20is%20systematic%20in%20its%20character%20and%20form%3A%20the%20mass%20displacement%20of%20the%20population%20of%20Gaza%2C%20herded%20into%20areas%20where%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20killed%2C%20and%20the%20deliberate%20creation%20of%20conditions%20that%20%E2%80%9Clead%20to%20a%20slow%20death%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20clear%20pattern%20of%20conduct%3A%20the%20targeting%20of%20family%20homes%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%2C%20laying%20waste%20to%20vast%20areas%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20bombing%2C%20shelling%20and%20sniping%20of%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20where%20they%20stand%2C%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20health%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20as%20we%20stand%20today%2C%201%25%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20in%20Gaza%20has%20been%20systematically%20decimated%2C%20and%20in%2040%20Gazans%20have%20been%20injured%2C%20since%207%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20elements%20alone%20are%20capable%20of%20evidencing%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20intent%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20whole%20or%20part%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20third%2C%20there%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20feature%20in%20this%20case%3A%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20political%20leaders%2C%20military%20commanders%20and%20persons%20holding%20official%20positions%20have%20systematically%20and%20in%20explicit%20terms%20declared%20their%20genocidal%20intent%3B%20and%20these%20statements%20are%20then%20repeated%20by%20soldiers%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Gaza%20as%20they%20engage%20in%20the%20destruction%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20show%20this%20third%20element%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntent%20from%20genocidal%20speeches%20by%20leaders%20and%20military%20officials%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20special%20genocidal%20intent%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20belief%20that%20in%20fact%20the%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20just%20the%20military%20wing%20of%20Hamas%2C%20or%20indeed%20Hamas%20generally%2C%20but%20is%20embedded%20in%20the%20fabric%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%207%20October%2C%20in%20a%20televised%20address%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20declared%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20and%20I%20quote%2C%20Israel%20had%20started%20%E2%80%9Cclear%5Bing%5D%20out%20the%20communities%20that%20have%20been%20infiltrated%20by%20terrorists%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20he%20warned%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%20price%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20paid%20by%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20Israel%20is%20the%20occupying%20power%2C%20in%20control%20of%20Gaza%3B%20it%20controls%20entry%2C%20exit%20and%20the%20internal%20movements%20of%20inside%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%C2%A0%3Cem%3Equa%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EPrime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20exercises%20overall%20command%20over%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Force%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%2C%20in%20his%20address%20to%20the%20Israeli%20forces%20on%2028%20October%202023%20%E2%80%94%20preparing%20for%20the%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20urged%20the%20soldiers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremember%20what%20Amalek%20has%20done%20to%20you%E2%80%9D.%20This%20refers%20to%20the%20Biblical%20command%20by%20God%20to%20Saul%20for%20the%20retaliatory%20destruction%20of%20an%20entire%20group%20of%20people%20known%20as%20the%20Amalekites%3A%20%E2%80%9CPut%20to%20death%20men%20and%20women%2C%20children%20and%20infants%2C%20cattle%20and%20sheep%2C%20camels%20and%20donkeys%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20genocidal%20invocation%20to%20Amalek%20was%20anything%20but%20idle.%20It%20was%20repeated%20by%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Israeli%20armed%20forces%20on%203%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Knesset%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Parliament%2C%20has%20called%20for%20the%20erasure%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Force%20agrees.%20On%209%20October%2C%20the%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20gave%20a%20%E2%80%98situation%20update%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20army%20where%20he%20said%20that%20as%20Israel%20was%20%E2%80%9Cimposing%20a%20complete%20siege%20on%20Gaza%E2%80%9D%3B%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20would%20be%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20food%2C%20no%20water%2C%20no%20fuel.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20would%20be%20closed%E2%80%9D%2C%20because%20Israel%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfighting%20human%20animals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20troops%20on%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%20he%20instructed%20them%20that%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Creleased%20all%20the%20restraints%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20won%E2%80%99t%20return%20to%20what%20it%20was%20before.%20We%20will%20eliminate%20everything%E2%80%A6%20we%20will%20reach%20all%20places.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEliminate%20everything.%20Reach%20all%20places.%20Without%20any%20restraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theme%20of%20destruction%20of%20%E2%80%9Chuman%20animals%E2%80%9D%20was%20reiterated%20by%20an%20Israeli%20Army%20Coordinator%20of%20Government%20Activities%20in%20the%20Territories%20(%E2%80%9CCOGAT%E2%80%9D)%20on%209%20October%202023%20who%20%E2%80%94%20in%20an%20address%20to%20%E2%80%9CHamas%20and%20the%20residents%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20stated%20that%20Hamas%20has%20become%20ISIS%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20citizens%20of%20Gaza%20are%20celebrating%20instead%20of%20being%20horrified%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9Chuman%20animals%20are%20dealt%20with%20accordingly%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20imposed%20a%20total%20blockade%20on%20Gaza%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20water%2C%C2%A0just%20damage.%20You%20wanted%20hell%2C%20you%20will%20get%20hell.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20of%20systematic%20dehumanisation%20is%20evident%20here%3A%20%E2%80%9Chuman%20animals%E2%80%9D.%20Both%20Hamas%20and%20civilians%20are%20condemned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20Israeli%20cabinet%2C%20this%20is%20also%20a%20widely%20held%20view.%20The%20Minister%20of%20Energy%20and%20Infrastructure%2C%20Israel%20Katz%2C%20called%20for%20the%20denial%20of%20water%20and%20fuel%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20a%20people%20of%20children%20killers%20and%20slaughterers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20admits%20of%20no%20ambiguity%3A%20it%20means%20to%20create%20conditions%20of%20death%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20die%20a%20slow%20death%20because%20of%20starvation%20and%20dehydration%20or%20to%20die%20quickly%20because%20of%20a%20bomb%20attack%20or%20snipers.%20But%20to%20die%2C%20nevertheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Heritage%20Minister%20Amichai%20Eliyahu%20said%20that%20Israel%20%E2%80%9Cmust%20find%20ways%20for%20Gazans%20that%20are%20more%20painful%20than%20death%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20no%20answer%20to%20say%20that%20neither%20are%20in%20command%20of%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20Ministers%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Government%3B%20they%20vote%20in%20the%20Knesset%3B%20and%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20shape%20State%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intent%20to%20destroy%20Gaza%20has%20been%20nurtured%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20State%2C%20as%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20has%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20those%20signing%20bombs%20destined%20for%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20having%20previously%20noted%20that%20the%20entire%20population%20of%20Gaza%20is%20responsible%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20rhetoric%20about%20civilians%20not%20aware%2C%20not%20involved%2C%20is%20absolutely%20not%20true%E2%80%A6%20we%20will%20fight%20until%20we%20break%20their%20backbone%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20attempts%20by%20the%20President%20and%20others%20to%20neutralise%20this%20speech%2C%20have%20not%20altered%20the%20sting%20of%20his%20words%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20to%20tar%20all%20Palestinians%2C%20as%20responsible%20for%20the%20actions%20of%20Hamas.%20Nor%2C%20as%20I%20will%20show%20below%2C%20has%20it%20affected%20how%20State%20policy%20is%20understood%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20of%20National%20Security%20repeated%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20statements%20that%20Hamas%20and%20civilians%20are%20responsible%20in%20equal%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2010%20November%202023%2C%20in%20a%20televised%20interview%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20we%20say%20that%20Hamas%20should%20be%20destroyed%2C%20it%20also%20means%20those%20who%20celebrate%2C%20those%20who%20support%2C%20and%20those%20who%20hand%20out%20candy%20%E2%80%93%20they%E2%80%99re%20all%20terrorists%2C%20and%20they%20should%20also%20be%20destroyed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20orders%20to%20destroy.%20And%20to%20maim%20what%20cannot%20be%20destroyed.%20These%20statements%20are%20not%20open%20to%20neutral%20interpretations%2C%20or%20after%20the%20fact%20rationalisations%20and%20re-interpretations%20by%20Israel.%20The%20statements%20were%20made%20by%20persons%20in%20command%20of%20the%20State.%20They%20communicated%20State%20policy.%20It%20is%20simple.%20If%20the%20statements%20were%20not%20intended%2C%20they%20would%20not%20have%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-south-africa-genocidal-acts-icj%5C%22%3EHarm%2C%20Calculation%2C%20Reproductive%20Violence%3A%20Why%20South%20Africa%20Feels%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Conduct%20in%20Gaza%20Is%20Genocide%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntent%20from%20genocidal%20speech%20by%20soldiers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20genocidal%20intent%20behind%20these%20statements%20is%20not%20ambiguous%20to%20the%20Israeli%20soldiers%20on%20the%20ground.%20Indeed%2C%20it%20is%20directing%20their%20actions%20and%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%207%20December%202023%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20proved%20that%20they%20understood%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20message%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremember%20what%20the%20Amalek%20has%20done%20to%20you%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20genocidal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20recorded%20by%20journalists%20dancing%20and%20singing%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20our%20motto%3A%20there%20are%20no%20uninvolved%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3B%20that%20they%20obey%20one%20commandment%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20wipe%20off%20the%20seed%20of%20Amalek%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20invocation%20of%20%E2%80%9CAmalek%E2%80%9D%20is%20being%20used%20by%20soldiers%20to%20justify%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%2C%20including%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20soldiers%20in%20Gaza%20were%20filmed%20dancing%2C%20chanting%2C%20and%20singing%20in%20November%20%E2%80%9CMay%20their%20Village%20burn%2C%20May%20Gaza%20be%20erased%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20now%20a%20trend%20among%20the%20soldiers%20to%20film%20themselves%20committing%20atrocities%20against%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20in%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Csnuff%E2%80%9D%20video.%20One%20recorded%20himself%20detonating%20over%2050%20houses%20in%20Shujaiya%3B%20other%20soldiers%20were%20recorded%20singing%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20destroy%20all%20of%20Khan%20Younes%20and%20this%20house%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20blow%20it%20up%20for%20you%20and%20for%20everything%20you%20do%20for%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commanders%20of%20the%20army%20are%20also%20of%20the%20same%20mind.%20Israeli%20army%20Commander%20Yair%20Ben%20David%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20army%20had%20done%20in%20%E2%80%9CBeit%20Hanoun%20and%20did%20there%20as%20Shimon%20and%20Levi%20did%20in%20Nablus%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bt%5Dhe%20entire%20Gaza%20should%20resemble%20Beit%20Hanoun%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20soldier%20Yishai%20Shalev%2C%20published%20a%20video%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20ruins%20of%20what%20was%20the%20site%20of%20Al%20Azhar%20University%20with%20the%20caption%20%E2%80%9Conce%20upon%20a%20time%20there%20was%20a%20university%20in%20Gaza%20and%20in%20practice%20%E2%80%93%20a%20school%20for%20murderers%20and%20human%20animals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20obviously%20believe%20that%20this%20language%20and%20their%20actions%20are%20acceptable%20because%20the%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20in%20Gaza%20is%20articulated%20State%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20political%20and%20military%20officials%20encouraged%20without%20censure%20the%2095-year-old%20Israeli%20army%20reservist%20Ezra%20Yachin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20veteran%20of%20the%20Deir%20Yassin%20massacre%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20in%201948%20%E2%80%94%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20soldiers%20ahead%20of%20the%20ground%20invasion%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20tour%2C%20he%20echoed%20the%20same%20sentiment%20while%20being%20driven%20around%20in%20an%20official%20Israeli%20army%20vehicle%2C%20dressed%20in%20Israeli%20army%20fatigues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBe%20triumphant%20and%20finish%20them%20off%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20leave%20anyone%20behind.%20%3Cem%3EErase%20the%20memory%20of%20them.%20Erase%20them%2C%20their%20families%2C%20mothers%20and%20children.%20These%20animals%20can%20no%20longer%20live%3C%2Fem%3E%20.%20.%20.%20If%20you%20have%20an%20Arab%20neighbour%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%2C%20go%20to%20his%20home%20and%20shoot%20him%20.%20.%20.%20We%20want%20to%20invade%2C%20not%20like%20before%2C%20we%20want%20to%20enter%20and%20destroy%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%20and%20destroy%20houses%2C%20then%20destroy%20the%20one%20after%20it.%20With%20all%20of%20our%20forces%2C%20complete%20destruction%2C%20enter%20and%20destroy.%20As%20you%20can%20see%2C%20we%20will%20witness%20things%20we%E2%80%99ve%20never%20dreamed%20of.%20%3Cem%3ELet%20them%20drop%20bombs%20on%20them%20and%20erase%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0As%20recently%20as%207%20January%202024%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20soldier%20was%20posted%20online%20where%20he%20boasts%20that%20the%20army%20had%20destroyed%20the%20entire%20village%20of%20Hirbet%20Ahza.%20For%20two%20weeks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20they%20had%20worked%20hard%20to%20bomb%20the%20village%20and%20executed%20their%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20suggestion%20that%20senior%20politicians%20did%20not%20mean%20what%20they%20said%2C%20much%20less%20that%20the%20meaning%20was%20not%20understood%20by%20soldiers%20in%20Gaza%2C%20would%20be%20without%20any%20merit.%20The%20scale%20of%20destruction%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20mass%20targeting%20of%20family%20homes%20and%20civilians%2C%20the%20war%20being%20%E2%80%9Ca%20war%20on%20children%E2%80%9D%2C%20all%20make%20clear%20that%20that%20genocidal%20intent%20is%20both%20understood%20and%20is%20being%20put%20into%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20articulated%20intent%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20in%20all%20its%20manifestations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntent%20from%20public%20incitement%20of%20genocide%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20genocidal%20rhetoric%20is%20also%20commonplace%20within%20the%20Israeli%20Knesset.%20Members%20of%20the%20Knesset%20(%E2%80%98MKs%E2%80%99)%20have%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20Gaza%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cwiped%20out%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cflatten%5Bed%5D%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceras%5Bed%5D%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9C%5Bc%5Drush%5Bed%5D%E2%80%A6%20on%20all%20its%20inhabitants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20deplored%20anyone%20%E2%80%9Cfeel%5Bing%5D%20sorry%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cuninvolved%E2%80%9D%20Gazans%2C%20asserting%20repeatedly%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20no%20uninvolved%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bt%5Dhere%20are%20no%20innocents%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20killers%20of%20the%20women%20and%20children%20should%20not%20be%20separated%20from%20the%20citizens%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20children%20of%20Gaza%20have%20brought%20this%20upon%20themselves%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20should%20be%20one%20sentence%20for%20everyone%20there%20%E2%80%94%20death%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20lawmakers%20have%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cmercilessly%E2%80%9D%20bombing%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20the%20air%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20some%20advocating%20for%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20(%E2%80%9Cdoomsday%E2%80%9D)%20weapons%2C%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9CNakba%20that%20will%20overshadow%20the%20Nakba%20of%2048%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20speech%20has%20gained%20ground%20among%20some%20elements%20of%20civil%20society.%20A%20famous%20singer%20has%20repeated%20Mr%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20Amalek%20reference%2C%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9CGaza%20must%20be%20wiped%20out%20and%20be%20destroyed%20with%20every%20Amalek%20seed%E2%80%A6%20we%20simply%20must%20destroy%20all%20of%20Gaza%20and%20exterminate%20everyone%20who%20is%20there%E2%80%9D%3B%20another%20has%20called%20to%20%E2%80%9CErase%20Gaza%2C%20not%20leave%20a%20single%20person%20there%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalists%20and%20commentators%20have%20announced%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20woman%20is%20an%20enemy%2C%20the%20baby%20is%20an%20enemy%E2%80%A6%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20is%20an%20enemy%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20%E2%80%9Cturn%20the%20strip%20into%20a%20slaughterhouse%E2%80%9D%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdemolish%20every%20house%20our%20soldiers%20come%20across%E2%80%9D.%20Exterminate%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intentional%20failure%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Israel%20to%20condemn%2C%20prevent%20and%20punish%20such%20genocidal%20incitement%20constitutes%20in%20itself%20a%20grave%20violation%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%20We%20should%20recall%20that%20in%20article%201%20of%20the%20Convention%2C%20Israel%20confirmed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%2C%20whether%20committed%20in%20time%20of%20peace%20or%20in%20time%20of%20war%2C%20is%20a%20crime%20under%20international%20law%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%20undertook%20%E2%80%9Cto%20prevent%20and%20to%20punish%E2%80%9D%20it%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20failure%20to%20prevent%2C%20condemn%20and%20punish%20such%20speech%20by%20the%20Government%20has%20served%20to%20normalise%20genocidal%20rhetoric%20and%20extreme%20danger%20for%20Palestinians%20within%20Israeli%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20MK%20Moshe%20Saada%2C%20from%20the%20Likud%20Party%2C%20has%20said%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20attorneys%20share%20his%20views%20that%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20must%20be%20destroyed%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20go%20anywhere%2C%20and%20they%20tell%20you%20to%20destroy%20them.%20In%20the%20Kibbutz%2C%20they%20tell%20you%20to%20destroy%20them%2C%20my%20friends%20at%20the%20State%20Attorney%E2%80%99s%20office%20who%E2%80%99ve%20fought%20with%20me%20on%20political%20issues%2C%20in%20debates%2C%20said%20to%20me%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99it%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20need%20to%20destroy%20all%20Gazans%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20Destroy%20all%20Gazans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnowledge%20of%20the%20destruction%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20aware%20of%20its%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20and%20infrastructure.%20Despite%20this%20knowledge%2C%20it%20has%20maintained%20%E2%80%93%20and%20indeed%20intensified%20%E2%80%93%20its%20military%20activity%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20full%20awareness%2C%20in%20the%20week%20after%207%20October%2C%20NGOs%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20warned%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%E2%80%9D%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cactors%20must%20allow%20humanitarian%20teams%20and%20goods%20to%20immediately%20and%20safely%20reach%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20need%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20Israel%20knew%20it%20was%20depriving%20water%2C%20food%2C%20electricity%20and%20essentials%20for%20survival.%20It%20said%20so%3A%20%E2%80%9Ceverything%20is%20closed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20known%20that%20it%20was%20depriving%20Palestinians%20of%20healthcare%20and%20treatment%20for%20injury%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20unprecedented%20bombardment%2C%20of%20food%20and%20water%2C%20and%20of%20other%20essentials%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20to%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20on%20our%20knees%20asking%20for%20sustained%2C%20scaled%20up%2C%20protected%20humanitarian%20operations%E2%80%9D%2C%20appealing%20%E2%80%9Cto%20all%20those%20in%20a%20situation%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20or%20influence%20decision%20makers%2C%20to%20give%20us%20the%20humanitarian%20space%20to%20address%20this%20human%20catastrophe%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20knowledge%2C%20Israel%20continues%20to%20target%20infrastructure%20essential%20for%20survival%3A%20water%20and%20sanitation%20infrastructure%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20bakeries%2C%20mills%2C%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20bombs%20hospitals%2C%20decimating%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20It%20targets%20aid%20workers%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20United%20Nations.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20the%20policy%20of%20Israel%20that%20Gaza%20became%20a%20place%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20and%20despair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20Madam%20President%2C%20many%20propagators%20of%20grave%20atrocities%20have%20protested%20that%20they%20were%20misunderstood%3B%20that%20they%20did%20not%20mean%20what%20they%20said%3B%20and%20that%20their%20own%20words%20were%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20What%20State%20would%20admit%20to%20a%20genocidal%20intent%3F%20Yet%2C%20the%20distinctive%20feature%20of%20this%20case%20has%20not%20been%20the%20silence%20as%20such%2C%20but%20the%20reiteration%20and%20repetition%20of%20genocidal%20speech%20throughout%20every%20sphere%20of%20State%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20remind%20the%20Court%20of%20the%20identity%20and%20authority%20of%20the%20genocidal%20inciters%3A%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3B%20the%20President%3B%20the%20Minister%20of%20Defence%3B%20the%20Minister%20of%20National%20Security%3B%20the%20Minister%20of%20Energy%20and%20Infrastructure%3B%20members%20of%20the%20Knesset%3B%20senior%20army%20officials%3B%20and%20foot%20soldiers.%20Genocidal%20utterances%20are%20therefore%20not%20out%20in%20the%20fringes%3B%20they%20are%20embodied%20in%20State%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intent%20to%20destroy%20is%20plainly%20understood%20by%20soldiers%20on%20the%20ground.%20It%20is%20also%20fully%20understood%20by%20some%20within%20the%20Israeli%20society%2C%20with%20the%20Government%20facing%20criticism%20for%20allowing%20in%20any%20aid%20to%20Gaza%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20it%20is%20recanting%20on%20its%20%E2%80%9Cpromise%E2%80%9D%20to%20starve%20Palestinians.%20Any%20suggestion%20that%20Israeli%20officials%20did%20not%20mean%20what%20they%20said%2C%20or%20were%20not%20fully%20understood%20%E2%80%94%20by%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20alike%20%E2%80%94%20to%20mean%20what%20they%20said%2C%20should%20be%20rejected%20by%20this%20Court.%20The%20evidence%20of%20genocidal%20intent%20is%20not%20only%20chilling%2C%20it%20is%20also%20overwhelming%20and%20incontrovertible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%20President%2C%20it%20is%20now%20my%20honour%20to%20request%20you%20to%20call%20Mr%20John%20Dugard%20SC%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-pos%3D%5C%22middle%5C%22%20data-embed24%3D%5C%22Oovvuu2%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-oovvuu-embed%3D%5C%22de390175-b983-42f1-b6ff-cbf3f37cb5c9%5C%22%20data-loaded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cem%3ETembeka%20Ngcukaitobi%2C%20advocate%20of%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20high%20court%2C%20presented%20the%20case%20for%20why%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20intent%20in%20Gaza%20can%20be%20clearly%20construed%20as%20genocidal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705054145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12153621%2FGDjloxcWoAAMcy9.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-south-africa-genocidal-intent-gaza-icj%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20articulated%20intent%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20in%20all%20its%20manifestations%2C'%20advocate%20Tembeka%20Ngcukaitobi%20said%20at%20the%20ICJ.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-south-africa-genocidal-intent-gaza-icj%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20to%20Singapore%20for%20my%20boyfriend%20and%20landed%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20my%20dream%20job.%20Then%20everything%20fell%20apart.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222277%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woma