ently%20holds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20several%20sitting%20MPs%20expressed%20a%20desire%20to%20not%20contest%20this%20election.%20It%20is%2C%20however%2C%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20ward%20off%20possible%20anti-incumbency%2C%20particularly%20in%20a%20state%20the%20party%20has%20performed%20well%20in%20over%20the%20past%20two%20general%20elections%3B%20in%202014%20the%20BJP%20won%2017%20seats%20(the%20Congress%20got%20nine)%20and%2C%20in%202019%2C%20it%20went%20eight%20better%20and%20cornered%20over%2051%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20not%20contesting%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20DV%20Sadananda%20Gowda%3B%20the%2070-year-old%20Bengaluru%20(North)%20MP%20in%20November%20said%20he%20was%20quitting%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGM%20Siddeswara%2C%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20the%20Davangere%20seat%20and%20ex-union%20minister%2C%20and%20Ramesh%20Jigajinagi%2C%20a%20six-time%20MP%20(three%20from%20Bijapur%20and%20three%20from%20Chikkodi%2C%20are%20also%20not%20up%20for%20re-election%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBachhe%20Gowda%20(Chikballapur)%2C%20GS%20Basavaraj%20(Tumkur)%2C%20V%20Srinivasa%20Prasad%20(Chamarajanagar)%2C%20and%20Y%20Devendrappa%20(Balar)%20may%20also%20not%20contest.%20Of%20all%20of%20them%2C%20the%20first%20three%20are%20over%2070%20years%20old%2C%20while%20Gowde%20is%2081%20years%20old%2C%20Basavaraj%20is%2082%2C%20Srinivasa%20Prasad%20is%2076%2C%20and%20Devendrappa%20is%2072.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnant%20Hegde%2C%20a%20four-time%20winner%20from%20Uttara%20Kannada%2C%20cited%20ill%20health%20in%20his%20request%2C%20and%20Shivkumar%20Udassi%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Haveri%20seat%20thrice%2C%20is%20also%20out.%20Both%20are%20younger%3B%20Udassi%20is%2056%20and%20Hegde%2055.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBroadly%20speaking%20the%20changes%20are%20in%20line%20with%20the%20BJP's%20(unwritten)%20rule%20-%20younger%20is%20better%20and%20three-time%20winners%20or%20above%20should%20give%20way%20to%20someone%20else%20(to%20avoid%20anti-incumbency).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20rule%2C%20though%2C%20has%20been%20set%20aside%20now%20and%20then%2C%20including%20in%202019%2C%20when%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20became%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20when%20he%20was%2076.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20there%20may%2C%20of%20course%2C%20be%20exceptions%20to%20this%20rule%20as%20the%20party%20preps%20for%20its%20'mission%202024'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBJP%20In%20Karnataka%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20thumped%20in%20last%20year's%20Karnataka%20Assembly%20election%2C%20with%20a%20Congress%20inspired%20by%20poll%20strategist%20Sunil%20Kanugolu%20coming%20up%20trumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-kanugolu-2024-lok-sabha-election-sunil-kanugolu-key-to-congress-telangana-win-not-part-of-2024-planning-4847776%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAhead%20Of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20Congress%20Loses%202nd%20Strategist%20After%20Prashant%20Kishor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanugolu%20may%20not%20be%20directing%20the%20Congress'%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20masterplan%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20will%20want%20to%20take%20no%20chances%20of%20a%20second%20consecutive%20defeat%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20the%20party%20has%20announced%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20but%2C%20as%20with%20any%20political%20alliance%2C%20specially%20one%20cobbled%20together%20between%20unequal%20members%20months%20before%20a%20critical%20election%2C%20seat-sharing%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20problematic%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20the%20JDS%20may%20get%20four%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20inclu