ristmas-eve%20'romance'%20between%20an%20unhappily%20married%20mother%20of%20a%20little%20wide-eyed%20girl%20(Pari%20Maheshwari%20Sharma)%20and%20a%20mysterious%20loner%20who%20returns%20to%20his%20Mumbai%20home%20after%20a%20long%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20as%20Hitchcockian%20in%20its%20unsettling%20twists%20and%20turns%20as%20it%20is%20Rohmerian%20in%20its%20sustained%20and%20piercingly%20unsentimental%20moral%20probe%20into%20the%20dynamics%20of%20love%2C%20loyalty%20and%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenplay%20by%20Raghavan%2C%20Arijit%20Biswas%2C%20Pooja%20Ladha%20Surti%20(also%20the%20film's%20editor)%20and%20Anukriti%20Pandey%20is%20littered%20with%20scattered%20clues%20that%20acquire%20increasing%20meaning%20as%20the%20plot%20unfolds%20in%20and%20around%20a%20woman's%20home%20situated%20above%20a%20family%20bakery%20that%20supplies%20butter%20biscuits%20to%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUUKdUNMgk7Q%3Fsi%3DkHFMxzdRrgSwMdL3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20there%20is%20only%20talk%20happening%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20or%20stray%20glances%20being%20exchanged%20between%20two%20strangers%20or%20just%20stretches%20of%20awkward%20silences%20are%20resorted%20to%20in%20trying%20to%20penetrate%20the%20distance%20that%20exists%20between%20Maria%20(Katrina%20Kaif)%20and%20Albert%20(Vijay%20Sethupathi)%2C%20the%20audience%20has%20so%20much%20to%20savour%20-%20and%20unpack%20-%20in%20this%20film%20that%20it%20does%20not%20for%20a%20moment%20feel%20either%20pretentious%20or%20unduly%20deliberate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%26lt%3Bp.patience%20in%3D%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%20is%3D%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%20key%3D%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%20the%3D%26quot%3B%26quot%3B%3EMerry%20Christmas%20for%20the%20two%20principal%20characters%20as%20well%20as%20the%20attentive%20watcher%20who%20is%20given%20a%20ringside%20view%20of%20the%20goings-on%20without%20everything%20being%20spelt%20out%20in%20black%20and%20white.%20Director%20of%20photography%20Madhu%20Neelakandan%20envelopes%20the%20residential%20interiors%20and%20the%20cityscapes%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20magic%20as%20everything%20in%20and%20around%20the%20frames%20that%20he%20composes%20suggests%20both%20festivity%20and%20enigma.%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatrina%20Kaif%2C%20in%20one%20of%20most%20convincing%20screen%20performances%20of%20her%20career%2C%20conveys%2C%20in%20a%20strikingly%20minimalistic%20manner%2C%20confusion%20and%20vulnerability%20cloaked%20in%20occasional%20flashes%20of%20steely%20determination.%20She%20is%20helped%20a%20great%20deal%20by%20the%20contrast%20that%20Vijay%20Sethupathi%20represents%20as%20an%20actor%20who%20relies%20more%20on%20his%20eyes%20and%20facial%20expressions%20than%20on%20mere%20words%20to%20capture%20the%20storm%20that%20is%20raging%20in%20his%20heart%20and%20mind%20and%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20a%20delightfully%20inventive%20cinematic%20ride%20that%20employs%20a%20very%201980s%20Hindi%20cinema%20soundscape%20and%20an%20evocative%20and%20transportive%20colour%20palette%20to%20generate%20a%20sense%20of%20bewilderment%20as%20the%20spectre%20of%20loneliness%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20lost%20love%20-%20both%20Maria%20and%20Albert%20have%20back%20stories%20that%20have%20brought%20them%20where%20they%20are%20at%20the%20outset%20of%20the%20film%20before%20the%20duo%20travels%20through%20the%20film's%20two-and-a-half-hour%20runtime%20in%20quest%20of%20a%20semblance%20of%20deliverance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaria%20and%20Albert%20ask%20questions%20of%20each%20other.%20The%20screenplay%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20comes%20up%20with%20posers%20for%20the%20audience%20-%20is%20violence%20indeed%20better%20than%20sacrifice%3F%20Are%20self-inflicted%20wounds%20morally%20more%20acceptable%20than%20seeking%20closure%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20somebody%20who%20has%20caused%20you%20pain%3F%20Can%20a%20brief%20encounter%20lead%20to%20a%20life-altering%20secret%20covenant%20between%20two%20individuals%20whose%20paths%20never%20cross%20until%20one%20fine%20evening%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20main%20characters%20exude%20a%20mix%20of%20serenity%20and%20mischief%20as%20they%20have%20a%20drink%20together%20in%20Maria's%20home%20and%20then%20go%20out%20for%20a%20walk%2C%20trading%20snatches%20of%20information%20that%20are%20aimed%20at%20helping%20each%20other%20break%20the%20ice%20and%20also%20at%20creating%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20clarity%20for%20the%20audience.%20But%20the%20latter%20effect%20is%20selective%20-%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20combination%20of%20obfuscation%20and%20revelation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffull-house-at-merry-christmas-screening-katrina-kaif-vicky-kaushal-ananya-panday-mrunal-thakur-and-others-4838325%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EMerry%20Christmas%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20firmly%20focused%20on%20Kaif%20and%20Sethupathi%2C%20but%20it%20does%20not%20let%20the%20secondary%20characters%20drift%20into%20any%20manner%20of%20insignificance%20irrespective%20of%20the%20length%20of%20time%20that%20they%20are%20on%20the%20screen.%20It%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20marvel%20that%20even%20an%20actor%20playing%20character%20who%20has%20only%20one%20almost%20inaudibly%20whispered%20line%20isn't%20just%20a%20footnote.%20He%20embodies%20the%20film's%20most%20significant%20turning%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeginning%20with%20Tinnu%20Anand's%20%26quot%3Bneighbour%20uncle%26quot%3B%20who%20gifts%20the%20prodigal%20Albert%20home-made%20wine%20on%20the%20day%20of%20his%20return%20and%20making%20its%20way%20through%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20'lifeless'%20Luke%20Kenny%20and%20a%20rakish%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%20as%20a%20caterer%20understandably%2