-strike-houthi-military-targets-in-yemen-13046682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faerial-footage-shows-moment-british-jets-strike-houthi-military-targets-in-yemen-13046682%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Faerial-footage-shows-moment-british-jets-strike-houthi-military-targets-in-yemen-13046682%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20may%20launch%20naval%20base%20in%20Georgian%20breakaway%20region%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705052860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106762697%2Cimgsize-24178.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-may-launch-naval-base-in-georgian-breakaway-region-in-2024%2Farticleshow%2F106762630.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106762630.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20Russian%20naval%20base%20in%20Abkhazia%2C%20a%20breakaway%20territory%20internationally%20recognised%20as%20part%20of%20Georgia%2C%20may%20become%20operational%20in%202024%2C%20Russian%20state%20news%20agency%20RIA%20quoted%20Abkhazia's%20security%20council%20as%20saying%20on%20Friday.Russian%20and%20Abkhazian%20authorities%20agreed%20in%20October%20that%20Russia%20could%20open%20a%20permanent%20naval%20base%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Ochamchire.RIA%20quoted%20the%20secretary%20of%20Abkhazia's%20security%20council%2C%20Sergei%20Shamba%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20construction%20of%20the%20base%20had%20not%20yet%20begun%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bits%20operation%20may%20begin%20this%20year%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-may-launch-naval-base-in-georgian-breakaway-region-in-2024%2Farticleshow%2F106762630.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-may-launch-naval-base-in-georgian-breakaway-region-in-2024%2Famp_articleshow%2F106762630.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-may-launch-naval-base-in-georgian-breakaway-region-in-2024%2Famp_articleshow%2F106762630.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Yatra%20Must%20Talk%20About%20Social%20Justice%20But%20Also%20Spiritual%20Justice%20for%20Shudras%2C%20Dalits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20former%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20starting%20his%20second%20%3Cem%3Eyatra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(march)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Maharashtra%20on%20January%2014%20.%20The%20first%20yatra%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%20was%20simply%20called%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20Its%20meaning%20and%20intent%20were%20very%20clear.%20There%20are%20different%20religions%20in%20India.%20But%20after%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Rastriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%2C%20were%20dismembered%20from%20the%20Indian%20civil%20society%20and%20state%20structures.%20A%20deep%20sense%20of%20de-secularising%20India%20was%20all%20over.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20were%20not%20ashamed%20of%20telling%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20world%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20un-Hindutva%2C%20thereby%20un-Indian.%20It%20managed%20elections%20by%20mobilising%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20along%20with%20Dwijas%20by%20telling%20them%20%E2%80%98let%20us%20rule%20ourselves%20by%20keeping%20the%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20out%20of%20power%20structures%20in%20all%20spheres%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20OBCs%20were%20convinced%20with%20this%20idea%20because%20they%20thought%20that%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule%2C%20the%20Dwijas%20and%20Muslim%20elite%20managed%20the%20power%20structures%20by%20neglecting%20the%20Shudras%2FOBCs.%20In%20reality%20also%2C%20from%20Nehru%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20the%20same%20pattern%20of%20power%20management%20continued.%20The%20Muslim%20elite%2C%20particularly%20Sunni%20Muslims%20who%20were%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20were%20completely%20kept%20out%20of%20power.%20Only%20few%20Shia%20Muslim%20elite%20were%20accommodated%20here%20and%20there.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20to%20reunite%20minorities%20in%20the%20Indian%20civil%20society.%20To%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20that%20yatra%20served%20its%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fhow-varna-and-jati-were-consolidated%5C%22%3EHow%20Varna%20and%20Jati%20Were%20Consolidated%20by%20Two%20Distinct%20Processes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20the%20BJP-RSS%2C%20while%20allowing%20some%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20and%20Dalits%20to%20be%20in%20formal%20power%20structures%2C%20are%20managing%20the%20real%20power%20with%20a%20high%20dose%20of%20monopoly%20capital%20accumulation%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Dwija%20capitalist-business%20forces.%20They%20are%20slowly%20driving%20the%20state%20to%20de-nationalise%20all%20major%20financial%20institutions.%20They%20plan%20to%20completely%20erase%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20through%20this.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Mandal%20movement%20achieved%20outside%20the%20ruling%20ideas%20of%20the%20RSS-BJP%20and%20Congress%20in%20the%201990s%20to%20deploy%20the%20institutional%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20with%20socially%20justifiable%20distribution%20of%20national%20resources%2C%20seats%20in%20the%20educational%20institutions%20and%20jobs%20in%20ruling%20structures.%20The%20RSS-BJP%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20systematically%20dismantle%20that%20social%20justice%20process.%20The%20Congress%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20did%20not%20bother%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20as%20they%20too%20did%20not%20want%20to%20recognise%20caste%20as%20a%20category%20of%20development.%20By%20showing%20the%20Congress-Muslim%20relationship%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20have%20drawn%20the%20Shudra%2FOBC%20into%20their%20fold%20and%20come%20to%20power.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransferring%20budget%20money%20to%20monopoly%20houses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20are%20following%20the%20American%20model%20of%20post-capitalist%20development%20by%20constructing%20massive%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20airports%2C%20seaports%20by%20transferring%20massive%20amounts%20of%20budget%20economy%20to%20contract%20capital%20to%20Dwija%20builders%20like%20Adanis%2C%20Ambanis%20and%20others%20by%20not%20allowing%20matching%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20reach%20the%20agrarian%20and%20artisanal%20forces%20with%20a%20theory%20that%20it%20is%20%3Cem%3Erevdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(freebee).%20More%20significantly%2C%20their%20direction%20is%20to%20de-reserve%20all%20jobs%20that%20are%20now%20going%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Shudra%2FOBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20through%20the%20route%20of%20privatisation%20and%20globalisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETowards%20these%20significant%20systemic%20directions%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20have%20already%20dropped%20the%20words%20secularism%20and%20socialism%20from%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20constitution%20without%20even%20amending%20it.%20If%20the%20concept%20of%20secularism%20was%20addressing%20social%20justice%20on%20the%20religious%20front%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20socialism%20was%20allowing%20India%20to%20expand%20the%20mass%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20part%20of%20which%20was%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20jobs.%20The%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20is%20closely%20related%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20socialism%20in%20India.%20But%20the%20Congress%20intellectuals%20always%20interpreted%20the%20idea%20of%20socialism%20only%20in%20the%20communist%20sense.%20Such%20an%20understanding%20did%20help%20the%20process%20of%20de-casteization%20of%20welfare%20and%20administration.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-bharat-jodo-yatra-modi-bjp%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notion%20of%20social%20justice%20has%20much%20deeper%20implications%20to%20dismantling%20the%20%3Cem%3Evarna%3C%2Fem%3E%20system%2C%20which%20RSS-BJP%20are%20expected%20to%20preserve.%20Its%20commitment%20to%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20or%20Rama%20Rajya%20includes%20protection%20to%20varna%20or%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20Congress%20has%20to%20redefine%20its%20old%20understanding%20%C2%A0of%20secularism%20and%20socialism%20to%20suit%20the%20Indian%20mode%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20challenge%20the%20RSS-BJP.%20Only%20then%20the%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20will%20shift%20towards%20them%20to%20safeguard%20their%20interests.%20They%20have%20to%20get%20deeper%C2%A0%20%C2%A0welfare%20schemes%20and%20protection%20to%20the%20constitutional%20guarantees%20of%20reservation%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes(STs)%20and%20OBCs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20realised%20this%20and%20gave%20a%20national%20call%20for%20enumeration%20of%20the%20Caste%20Census%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20to%20protect%20social%20justice%20and%20deepen%20it.%20The%20Congress%20has%20to%20take%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%20to%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20tribal%20society%20in%20the%20North%20East%20in%20this%20yatra.%20In%20the%20plains%2C%20starting%20from%20Bengal%20to%20Maharashtra%20it%20has%20to%20address%20caste%20society%20to%20remove%20inequalities.%20Their%20position%20has%20to%20be%20different%20from%20the%20position%20of%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20engineering%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP-RSS.%20Social%20engineering%20is%20not%20social%20justice.%20It%20is%20a%20mechanism%20to%20numb%20the%20consciousness%20of%20the%20Shudras%20and%20Dalits%20and%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20caste%20system%20is%20not%20bad.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20must%20repeatedly%20tell%20rural%20masses%20as%20part%20of%20the%20yatra%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20stand%20for%20the%20reservation%20system%20and%20stand%20against%20de-nationalisation%20of%20major%20government%20assets%20and%20it%20will%20stand%20for%20spiritual%20justice.%20Silence%20about%20spiritual%20injustice%20in%20the%20name%20of%20secularism%20does%20not%20appeal%20to%20the%20Shudras%20and%20Dalits.%20They%20too%20want%20the%20right%20to%20priesthood%20in%20Ram%20temple%20being%20inaugurated%20on%20January%2022.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20no%20position%20on%20such%20spiritual%20justice%20questions.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-yatra-achievement-goals%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20Achieved%20What%20It%20Set%20Out%20to%20Do%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20government%2C%20while%20doing%20the%20temple%20construction%20and%20inauguration%20as%20state%20work%2C%20has%20not%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20every%20caste-Hindu%20is%20equal%20and%20any%20person%20irrespective%20of%20caste%20could%20become%20a%20priest%20there.%20They%20did%20not%20say%20before%20the%20deity%20there%20is%20no%20Brahmin%2C%20no%20Chamar%3B%20a%20human%20is%20human.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnti-caste%20ideology%20encompasses%20spiritual%20justice%20to%20the%20historically%20oppressed%20Shudras%20and%20Dalits%20at%20least%20now%2C%20in%20the%20modern%20times%20in%20the%20system%20of%20political%20democracy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20Kashmir%20question%20of%20BJP-RSS%20ideology%20is%20a%20concern%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world%2C%20the%20Manipur%20massacre%20became%20a%20concern%20of%20the%20Western%20Christians.%20The%20yatra%20is%20going%20to%20start%20from%20that%20wounded%20civil%20society%20of%20Manipur.%20It%20has%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20work%20to%20heal%20such%20deeply%20struck%20wounds%20and%20preserve%20their%20Right%20to%20Religion%20which%20has%20certainly%20to%20do%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20spiritual%20justice%20in%20India.%20The%20idea%20of%20spiritual%20justice%20is%20universal%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20national.%C2%A0%20All%20parties%20and%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%2C%20Congress%2C%20RSS%20%E2%80%93%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20idea%20of%20universal%20spiritual%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP-RSS%20do%20not%20care%20for%20spiritual%20justice%20within%20the%20caste%20civil%20society%2C%20which%20they%20define%20as%20Hindu.%20The%20question%20of%20their%20caring%20for%20spiritual%20justice%20for%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20societies%20does%20not%20arise%20because%20they%20consider%20those%20religions%20as%20foreign%20and%20anti-national.%20No%20Dwija%20intellectual%20or%20political%20party%20leader%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20spiritual%20justice%20in%20India.%20Caste%20system%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20But%20it%20is%20time%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20to%20re-invoke%20the%20spirit%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%20to%20save%20India%20from%20the%20present%20situation%20from%20the%20point%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20spiritual%20justice%20to%20all%20castes%20and%20religions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EKancha%20Ilaiah%20Shepherd%20is%20a%20political%20theorist%2C%20social%20activist%20and%20author.%20His%20latest%20books%20are%20the%20Clash%20of%20Cultures%E2%80%94Productive%20Masses%20Vs%20Hindutva%20Mullah%20Conflicting%20Ethics%20and%20The%20Shudra%E2%80%94Vision%20For%20a%20New%20Path.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705052771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-must-talk-about-social-justice-but-also-spiritual-justice-for-shudras-dalits%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20will%20never%20talk%20about%20priesthood%20for%20anyone%20but%20Brahmins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Frahul-gandhis-yatra-must-talk-about-social-justice-but-also-spiritual-justice-for-shudras-dalits%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20It's%20Crucial%20to%20Understand%20That%20Hindu%20Pride%20Goes%20Beyond%20the%20Modi%20Factor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12151034%2Fimage-1727.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assertion%20that%20Hindus%2C%20particularly%20non-resident%20Indians%20(NRIs)%2C%20only%20started%20taking%20pride%20in%20their%20identity%20and%20culture%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20multifaceted%20argument%20that%20demands%20nuanced%20analysis.%20While%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20ascent%20has%20undoubtedly%20amplified%20and%20shaped%20Hindu%20and%20Indian%20cultural%20expression%2C%20attributing%20its%20emergence%20solely%20to%20his%20tenure%2C%20simplifies%20a%20complex%20phenomenon%20rooted%20in%20historical%2C%20social%2C%20and%20political%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20recognise%20that%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20cultural%20and%20religious%20identity%20existed%20among%20Hindus%20long%20before%20Modi.%20Throughout%20history%2C%20Hinduism%20has%20absorbed%20and%20co-existed%20with%20diverse%20influences%2C%20evolving%20within%20India%20and%20spreading%20through%20trade%20and%20religious%20exchange.%20Movements%20like%20Bhakti%20and%20reformist%20movements%20of%20the%2019th%20century%20rekindled%20pride%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20philosophical%20and%20cultural%20heritage.%20The%20struggle%20for%20independence%20fuelled%20national%20and%20cultural%20consciousness%2C%20with%20leaders%20like%20Gandhi%20drawing%20inspiration%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20spiritual%20traditions.%20Numerous%20luminaries%2C%20such%20as%20Swami%20Vivekananda%2C%20actively%20promoted%20Indian%20culture%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20long%20before%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20independence%2C%20India%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20of%20nation-building%2C%20prioritising%20secularism%20and%20unity%20amidst%20diverse%20religious%20and%20cultural%20landscapes.%20While%20Hindu%20identity%20remained%20integral%2C%20it%20was%20often%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20emphasis%20on%20national%20unity%20and%20modernisation.%20This%2C%20coupled%20with%20social%20and%20economic%20challenges%2C%20led%20to%20a%20certain%20downplaying%20of%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20particularly%20among%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20urban%20elite%20and%20NRIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20late%2020th%20and%20early%2021st%20centuries%20witnessed%20a%20resurgence%20of%20interest%20in%20Hindu%20traditions%20and%20cultural%20practices.%20This%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20several%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobalisation%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20diasporic%20communities%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20NRIs%20and%20Hindus%20globally%20encountered%20Western%20cultural%20norms%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20cultural%20difference%20and%20belonging%20emerged.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20renewed%20interest%20in%20their%20heritage%2C%20customs%2C%20and%20spiritual%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20quest%20for%20identity%20and%20belonging%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20world%20increasingly%20characterised%20by%20individualism%20and%20anomie%2C%20many%20found%20solace%20and%20community%20in%20their%20shared%20religious%20and%20cultural%20heritage.%20This%20was%20particularly%20true%20for%20younger%20generations%20seeking%20a%20sense%20of%20grounding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisillusionment%20with%20secularism%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20perceived%20failure%20of%20secularism%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20social%20inequality%20and%20religious%20intolerance%20led%20some%20to%20seek%20alternative%20solutions%20grounded%20in%20their%20cultural%20and%20religious%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20and%20Hindutva%20ideology%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20with%20its%20emphasis%20on%20Hindu%20identity%20and%20cultural%20resurgence%2C%20provided%20a%20platform%20for%20Hindus%20to%20express%20their%20pride%20and%20assert%20their%20political%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20growth%20and%20confidence%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20economic%20boom%20under%20Modi%20coincided%20with%20a%20rise%20in%20national%20pride%20and%20confidence.%20This%20sense%20of%20progress%20and%20achievement%20spilled%20over%20into%20cultural%20spheres%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20celebration%20of%20Indian%20heritage%2C%20including%20its%20Hindu%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20and%20digital%20platforms%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20social%20media%20provided%20a%20platform%20for%20Hindus%2C%20particularly%20younger%20generations%2C%20to%20connect%2C%20share%20experiences%2C%20and%20advocate%20for%20their%20identity.%20This%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20amplified%20voices%20previously%20unheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20undoubtedly%20amplified%20these%20trends%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20avoid%20attributing%20the%20resurgence%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20solely%20to%20his%20persona%20or%20policies.%20Modi%20himself%20is%20a%20product%20of%20these%20broader%20sociocultural%20currents%2C%20with%20his%20Hindu%20identity%20and%20rhetoric%20resonating%20with%20a%20pre-existing%20desire%20for%20self-assertion%20among%20a%20segment%20of%20the%20Hindu%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20rise%20capitalised%20on%20these%20existing%20currents.%20His%20political%20messaging%20resonated%20with%20Hindus%20seeking%20a%20stronger%20sense%20of%20identity%20and%20belonging.%20He%20emphasised%20India%E2%80%99s%20ancient%20cultural%20glory%2C%20invoking%20historical%20figures%20and%20symbols%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fg20-summit-pragati-maidan-speech-pm-modi-topra-ashokan-pillar-verse-2433394-2023-09-09%5C%22%3EAshoka%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fyoga-is-indias-gift-to-the-world-pm-narendra-modi-on-international-yoga-day%2Fvideoshow%2F69884149.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eyoga%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20positioned%20a%20resurgent%20India%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-is-vishwaguru-to-spin-dictators-the-world-over%5C%22%3Eworld%20stage%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20showcasing%20its%20economic%20potential%20and%20technological%20prowess.%20This%20narrative%20of%20cultural%20and%20economic%20revival%20resonated%20with%20the%20NRIs%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20had%20achieved%20success%20in%20their%20adopted%20countries%20but%20also%20cherished%20their%20cultural%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20government%20actively%20engaged%20with%20the%20diaspora%2C%20organising%20events%20and%20initiatives%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fwhy-pravasi-bharatiya-divas-is-celebrated-its-history-theme-and-significance-11704735561384.html%5C%22%3EPravasi%20Bharatiya%20Divas%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20fostered%20a%20sense%20of%20connection%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20complexities%20and%20potential%20pitfalls%20of%20linking%20national%20identity%20solely%20with%20religious%20identity.%20While%20highlighting%20India%E2%80%99s%20historical%20Hindu%20roots%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20marginalising%20other%20religious%20and%20cultural%20groups.%20This%20tendency%20towards%20Hindu%20nationalism%20raises%20concerns%20about%20inclusivity%20and%20tolerance%2C%20core%20values%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20attributing%20India%E2%80%99s%20success%20solely%20to%20its%20Hindu%20heritage%20risks%20erasing%20the%20contributions%20of%20other%20communities%20that%20have%20enriched%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20tapestry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-the-bjp-the-hindu-card-is-no-longer-as-potent-as-it-once-was%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Card%20Is%20No%20Longer%20as%20Potent%20as%20It%20Once%20Was%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20under%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20under%20Modi%20is%20also%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20global%20trend%20of%20identity%20politics%20and%20cultural%20assertiveness.%20From%20Brexit%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20right-wing%20populism%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20we%20see%20communities%20reaffirming%20their%20cultural%20distinctiveness.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20experience%20aligns%20with%20a%20larger%20political%20shift%20rather%20than%20being%20solely%20attributable%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20a%20holistic%20understanding%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20goes%20beyond%20a%20singular%20political%20figure.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20intricate%20interplay%20of%20historical%20context%2C%20social%20anxieties%2C%20the%20yearning%20for%20global%20recognition%2C%20and%20the%20appeal%20of%20a%20confident%20leader%20promoting%20a%20revitalised%20national%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20of%20Hindu%20pride%20in%20the%20post-Modi%20era%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20a%20simple%20one%20of%20unalloyed%20positivity%20or%20negativity.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20complex%20tapestry%20woven%20with%20threads%20of%20historical%20legacy%2C%20diasporic%20experiences%2C%20sociopolitical%20shifts%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20specific%20political%20ideology.%20To%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20move%20beyond%20simplistic%20cause-and-effect%20explanations%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20rich%20and%20complex%20history%20of%20Hindu%20identity%2C%20its%20diverse%20expressions%2C%20and%20its%20evolving%20role%20in%20contemporary%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20Hindu%20pride%20is%20not%20monolithic.%20It%20manifests%20in%20various%20ways%2C%20from%20practicing%20yoga%20and%20celebrating%20festivals%20to%20advocating%20for%20social%20reforms%20within%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20NRIs%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20experience%20a%20unique%20blend%20of%20cultural%20influences%20and%20identities%2C%20leading%20to%20diverse%20expressions%20of%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20often%20characterised%20by%20a%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20their%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20surge%20in%20Hindu%20pride%20reflects%20a%20positive%20affirmation%20of%20identity%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20address%20the%20potential%20pitfalls.%20The%20association%20of%20Hindu%20identity%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%20has%20led%20to%20concerns%20about%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20majoritarianism%2C%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20other%20religious%20and%20cultural%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20challenge%20lies%20in%20ensuring%20that%20cultural%20pride%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20morph%20into%20exclusionary%20nationalism.%20India%E2%80%99s%20strength%20lies%20in%20its%20rich%20diversity%2C%20and%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20its%20historical%20and%20cultural%20heritage%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20inclusively%2C%20allowing%20all%20communities%20to%20flourish%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20vibrant%20tapestry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20leave%20you%20with%20these%20words%20of%20Hindi%20poet%20Abhi%20Munde%2C%20as%20posted%20on%20the%20YouTube%20channel%20Psycho%20Shayar%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYe%20tum%20logon%20ke%20Ram%20japon%20mein%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPehlay%20sa%20aaraam%20nahin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EZabardasti%20ke%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20mein%20sab%20kuch%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBus%20Ram%20nahin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(In%20your%20chants%20of%20Ram%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20comfort%20is%20missing%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20forced%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20everything%2C%20but%20Ram)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToh%20soch%20samajh%20kar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20kaho%20tum%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(So%2C%20think%20before%20you%20take%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20name)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5