onstrued%20as%20genocidal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20is%20her%20submission%20in%20full.%20Almost%20each%20line%20of%20the%20original%20text%20carries%20a%20footnote.%20The%20Wire%20has%20removed%20them%20for%20ease%20of%20reading.%20The%20original%20text%20and%20annotations%20are%20available%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcase-related%2F192%2F192-20240111-ora-01-00-bi.pdf%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenocidal%20acts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you.%20Madam%20President%2C%20distinguished%20Members%20of%20the%20Court%2C%20it%20is%20a%20privilege%20to%20appear%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20South%20Africa%20in%20this%20case%20of%20exceptional%20importance.%20It%20is%20a%20case%20that%20underscores%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20our%20shared%20humanity%20as%20expressed%20in%20the%20preamble%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20my%20task%20to%20address%20the%20Court%20on%20the%20genocidal%20acts%20that%20have%20led%20to%20this%20urgent%20request%20for%20provisional%20measures%20under%20Article%2041%20of%20the%20Statute%20of%20the%20Court.%20South%20Africa%20contends%20that%20Israel%20has%20transgressed%20Article%20II%20of%20the%20Convention%2C%20by%20committing%20actions%20that%20fall%20within%20the%20definition%20of%20genocide.%20The%20actions%20show%20a%20systematic%20pattern%20of%20conduct%20from%20which%20genocide%20can%20be%20inferred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOverview%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllow%20me%20to%20place%20these%20acts%20in%20context.%20Gaza%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20constituent%20territories%20of%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%2C%20occupied%20by%20Israel%20since%201967.%20It%20is%20a%20narrow%20strip%2C%20of%20approximately%20365%20sq%20km%2C%20as%20depicted%20in%20the%20map%20now%20displayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20continues%20to%20exercise%20control%20over%20the%20airspace%2C%20territorial%20waters%2C%20land%20crossings%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20electromagnetic%20sphere%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%20in%20Gaza%2C%20as%20well%20as%20over%20key%20governmental%20functions.%20As%20the%20honourable%20minister%20has%20said%2C%20entry%20and%20exit%20by%20air%20and%20sea%20to%20Gaza%20is%20prohibited%20with%20Israel%20operating%20the%20only%20two%20crossing%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%20in%20the%20world%20is%20home%20to%20approximately%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20them%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2096%20days%2C%20Israel%20has%20subjected%20Gaza%20to%20what%20has%20been%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20heaviest%20conventional%20bombing%20campaigns%20in%20the%20history%20of%20modern%20warfare.%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20are%20being%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20weaponry%20and%20bombs%20from%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20also%20at%20immediate%20risk%20of%20death%20by%20starvation%2C%20dehydration%20and%20disease%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20ongoing%20siege%20by%20Israel%2C%20the%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20towns%2C%20the%20insufficient%20aid%20being%20allowed%20through%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20and%20the%20impossibility%20of%20distributing%20this%20limited%20aid%20while%20bombs%20fall.%20This%20conduct%20renders%20essentials%20to%20life%20unobtainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20provisional%20measures%20stage%2C%20as%20this%20Court%20has%20made%20clear%20in%20The%20Gambia%20v.%20Myanmar%20case%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20Court%20to%20come%20to%20a%20final%20view%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20constitutes%20genocide.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20establish%20only%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20.%20.%20.%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20acts%20alleged%20.%20.%20.%20are%20capable%20of%20falling%20within%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Convention%E2%80%9D.%20On%20analysing%20the%20specific%20and%20ongoing%20genocidal%20acts%20complained%20of%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20at%20least%20some%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20these%20acts%20fall%20within%20the%20Convention%E2%80%99s%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20acts%20are%20documented%20in%20detail%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Application%20and%20confirmed%20by%20reliable%2C%20often%20United%20Nations%2C%20sources.%20It%20is%20thus%20unnecessary%20and%20impossible%20for%20me%20to%20recount%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20highlight%20only%20some%20in%20order%20to%20illustrate%20the%20pattern%20of%20genocidal%20conduct.%20The%20United%20Nations%20statistics%20that%20are%20relied%20upon%20are%20up%20to%20date%20as%20of%209%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20oral%20submissions%2C%20we%20will%20illustrate%20the%20facts%20that%20we%20rely%20on%20with%20limited%20use%20of%20audiovisual%20material.%20Madam%20President%2C%20we%20do%20so%20with%20restraint%20and%20only%20where%20necessary%2C%20and%20always%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20background%2C%20I%20move%20now%20to%20demonstrate%20in%20turn%20how%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20violates%20Articles%20II%20(a)%2C%20II%20(b)%2C%20II%20(c)%20and%20II%20(d)%20of%20the%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20genocidal%20acts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArticle%20II%20(a)%3A%20killing%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20genocidal%20act%20committed%20by%20Israel%20is%20the%20mass%20killing%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%20II%20(a)%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20UN%20Secretary-General%20explained%20five%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20level%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20killing%20is%20so%20extensive%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnowhere%20is%20safe%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20stand%20before%20you%20today%2C%2023%2C210%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20during%20the%20sustained%20attacks%20over%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20at%20least%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20whom%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20women%20and%20children.%20Some%207%2C000%20Palestinians%20are%20still%20missing%2C%20presumed%20dead%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinians%20in%20Gaza%20are%20subjected%20to%20relentless%20bombing%20wherever%20they%20go.%20They%20are%20killed%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20in%20places%20where%20they%20seek%20shelter%2C%20in%20hospitals%2C%20in%20schools%2C%20in%20mosques%2C%20in%20churches%20and%20as%20they%20try%20to%20find%20food%20and%20water%20for%20their%20families.%20They%20have%20been%20killed%20if%20they%20failed%20to%20evacuate%2C%20in%20the%20places%20to%20which%20they%20have%20fled%20and%20even%20while%20they%20attempted%20to%20flee%20along%20Israeli%20declared%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20routes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20killing%20is%20so%20extensive%20that%20those%20whose%20bodies%20are%20found%20are%20buried%20in%20mass%20graves%2C%20often%20unidentified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20three%20weeks%20alone%20following%207%20October%2C%20Israel%20deployed%206%2C000%20bombs%20per%20week.%20At%20least%20200%20times%2C%20it%20has%20deployed%20two-thousand-pound%20bombs%20in%20southern%20areas%20of%20Palestine%20designated%20as%20%E2%80%9Csafe%E2%80%9D.%20These%20bombs%20have%20also%20decimated%20the%20north%2C%20including%20refugee%20camps.%20Two-thousand-pound%20bombs%20are%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20destructive%20bombs%20available.%20They%20are%20dropped%20by%20lethal%20fighter%20jets%20that%20are%20used%20to%20strike%20targets%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20by%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20resourced%20armies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20killed%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunparalleled%20and%20unprecedented%E2%80%9D%20number%20of%20civilians%2C%20with%20the%20full%20knowledge%20of%20how%20many%20civilian%20lives%20each%20bomb%20will%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201%2C800%20Palestinian%20families%20in%20Gaza%20have%20lost%20multiple%20family%20members%20and%20hundreds%20of%20multigenerational%20families%20have%20been%20wiped%20out%2C%20with%20no%20remaining%20survivors%20%E2%80%94%20mothers%2C%20fathers%2C%20children%2C%20siblings%2C%20grandparents%2C%20aunts%2C%20cousins%20%E2%80%94%20often%20all%20killed%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20killing%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20destruction%20of%20Palestinian%20life.%20It%20is%20inflicted%20deliberately.%20No%20one%20is%20spared%2C%20not%20even%20newborn%20babies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20Palestinian%20child%20killings%20in%20Gaza%20is%20such%20that%20United%20Nations%20chiefs%20have%20described%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20graveyard%20for%20children%E2%80%9D.%20The%20devastation%2C%20we%20submit%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20and%20has%20laid%20waste%20to%20Gaza%20beyond%20any%20acceptable%20legal%2C%20let%20alone%20humane%2C%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArticle%20II%20(b)%3A%20causing%20serious%20mental%20and%20bodily%20harm%20to%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20genocidal%20act%20identified%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Application%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20infliction%20of%20serious%20bodily%20or%20mental%20harm%20to%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%20II%20(b)%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20have%20left%20close%20to%2060%2C000%20Palestinians%20wounded%20and%20maimed%20%E2%80%93%20again%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children.%20This%20in%20circumstances%20where%20the%20healthcare%20system%20has%20all%20but%20collapsed.%20I%20return%20to%20this%20later%20in%20my%20speech.%20Large%20numbers%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20including%20children%20are%20arrested%2C%20blindfolded%2C%20forced%20to%20undress%20and%20loaded%20onto%20trucks%2C%20taken%20to%20unknown%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suffering%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20physical%20and%20mental%20%E2%80%93%20is%20undeniable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArticle%20II%20(c)%3A%20deliberately%20inflicting%20on%20the%20group%20conditions%20of%20life%20calculated%20to%20bring%20about%20its%20physical%20destruction%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20to%20the%20third%20genocidal%20act%2C%20under%20Article%20II%20(c)%3A%20Israel%20has%20deliberately%20imposed%20conditions%20on%20Gaza%20that%20cannot%20sustain%20life%20and%20are%20calculated%20to%20bring%20about%20its%20physical%20destruction.%20Israel%20achieves%20this%20in%20at%20least%20four%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20by%20displacement.%20Israel%20has%20forced%20the%20displacement%20of%20about%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%20There%20is%20nowhere%20safe%20for%20them%20to%20flee%20to%20%E2%80%93%20those%20who%20cannot%20leave%20or%20refuse%20to%20be%20displaced%20have%20either%20been%20killed%20or%20are%20at%20extreme%20risk%20of%20being%20killed%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20displaced%20multiple%20times%2C%20as%20families%20are%20forced%20to%20move%20repeatedly%20in%20search%20of%20safety.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20first%20evacuation%20order%20on%2013%20October%20required%20the%20evacuation%20of%20over%201%20million%20people%20%E2%80%94%20including%20children%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20the%20wounded%20and%20infirm%3B%20entire%20hospitals%20were%20required%20to%20evacuate%2C%20even%20newborn%20babies%20in%20intensive%20care.%20The%20order%20required%20them%20to%20evacuate%20the%20north%20to%20the%20south%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20itself%20was%20genocidal.%20It%20required%20immediate%20movement%2C%20taking%20only%20what%20could%20be%20carried%2C%20while%20no%20humanitarian%20assistance%20was%20permitted%2C%20and%20fuel%2C%20water%20and%20food%20and%20other%20necessities%20of%20life%20had%20deliberately%20been%20cut%20off.%20It%20was%20clearly%20calculated%20to%20bring%20about%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20Palestinians%2C%20the%20forced%20evacuation%20from%20their%20homes%20is%20inevitably%20permanent.%20Israel%20has%20now%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20an%20estimated%20355%2C000%20Palestinian%20homes%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20at%20least%20half%20a%20million%20Palestinians%20with%20no%20home%20to%20return%20to.%20The%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20explains%20that%20houses%20and%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20razed%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20frustrating%20any%20realistic%20prospects%20for%20displaced%20Gazans%20to%20return%20home%2C%20repeating%20a%20long%20history%20of%20mass%20forced%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%20by%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20indication%20at%20all%20that%20Israel%20accepts%20responsibility%20for%20rebuilding%20what%20it%20has%20destroyed.%20Instead%2C%20the%20destruction%20is%20celebrated%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%3A%20soldiers%20film%20themselves%20joyfully%20detonating%20entire%20apartment%20blocks%20and%20town%20squares%3B%20erecting%20the%20Israeli%20flag%20over%20the%20wreckage%2C%20seeking%20to%20re-establish%20Israeli%20settlements%20on%20the%20rubble%20of%20Palestinian%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20thus%20extinguishing%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20Palestinian%20life%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20together%20with%20the%20forced%20displacement%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20has%20been%20deliberately%20calculated%20to%20cause%20widespread%20hunger%2C%20dehydration%20and%20starvation.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20has%20pushed%20Gazans%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20famine.%20An%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%2093%25%20of%20the%20population%20in%20Gaza%20is%20facing%20crisis%20levels%20of%20hunger%E2%80%9D.%20Of%20all%20the%20people%20in%20the%20world%20currently%20suffering%20catastrophic%20hunger%2C%20more%20than%2080%20per%20cent%20are%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20situation%20is%20such%20that%20the%20experts%20are%20now%20predicting%20that%20more%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20may%20die%20from%20starvation%20and%20disease%20than%20airstrikes%20and%20yet%20Israel%20continues%20to%20impede%20the%20effective%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20Palestinians%2C%20not%20only%20refusing%20to%20allow%20sufficient%20aid%20in%2C%20but%20removing%20the%20ability%20to%20distribute%20it%20through%20constant%20bombardment%20and%20obstruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20on%208%20January%2C%20a%20planned%20mission%20by%20United%20Nations%20agencies%20to%20deliver%20urgent%20medical%20supplies%20and%20vital%20fuel%20to%20a%20hospital%20and%20medical%20supply%20centre%20was%20denied%20by%20Israeli%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marked%20the%20fifth%20denial%20of%20a%20mission%20to%20the%20centre%20since%2026%20December%2C%20leaving%20five%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20without%20access%20to%20life-saving%20medical%20supplies%20and%20equipment.%20Aid%20trucks%20that%20are%20allowed%20in%20are%20seized%20upon%20by%20the%20hungry.%20What%20is%20provided%20is%20simply%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%5BVideo%20playing%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%20President%2C%20Members%20of%20the%20Court%2C%20this%20is%20an%20image%20of%20an%20aid%20truck%20arriving%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Israel%20has%20deliberately%20inflicted%20conditions%20in%20which%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20are%20denied%20adequate%20shelter%2C%20clothes%20or%20sanitation.%20For%20weeks%2C%20there%20have%20been%20acute%20shortages%20of%20clothes%2C%20bedding%2C%20blankets%20and%20critical%20non-food%20items.%20Clean%20water%20is%20all%20but%20gone%2C%20leaving%20far%20below%20the%20amount%20required%20to%20safely%20drink%2C%20clean%20and%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20WHO%20has%20stated%20that%20Gaza%20is%20%E2%80%9Cexperiencing%20soaring%20rates%20of%20infectious%20disease%20outbreaks%E2%80%9D.%20Cases%20of%20diarrhoea%20in%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20have%20increased%202%2C000%20per%20cent%20since%20hostilities%20began.%20When%20combined%20and%20left%20untreated%2C%20malnutrition%20and%20disease%20create%20a%20deadly%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20genocidal%20act%20under%20Article%20II%20(b)%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20assault%20on%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%2C%20which%20renders%20life%20unsustainable.%20Even%20by%207%20December%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20the%20right%20to%20health%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5Bt%5Dhe%20healthcare%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20has%20been%20completely%20obliterated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20wounded%20by%20Israel%20in%20Gaza%20are%20being%20deprived%20of%20life-saving%20medical%20care.%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20%E2%80%93%20already%20crippled%20by%20years%20of%20blockade%20and%20prior%20attacks%20by%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20is%20unable%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20the%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Article%20II%20(d)%3A%20reproductive%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Special%20Rapporteur%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%20has%20pointed%20to%20acts%20committed%20by%20Israel%20that%20would%20fall%20under%20the%20fourth%20category%20of%20genocidal%20acts%2C%20in%20Article%20II%20(d)%20of%20the%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2022%20November%20she%20expressly%20warned%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20reproductive%20violence%20inflicted%20by%20Israel%20on%20Palestinian%20women%2C%20newborn%20babies%2C%20infants%2C%20and%20children%20could%20be%20qualified%20as%20.%20.%20.%20acts%20of%20genocide%20under%20Article%202%20of%20the%20%5BGenocide%20Convention%5D%20.%20.%20.%20including%20%E2%80%98imposing%20measures%20intended%20to%20prevent%20births%20within%20a%20group%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20blocking%20the%20delivery%20of%20life-saving%20aid%2C%20including%20essential%20medical%20kits%20for%20delivering%20babies%2C%20in%20circumstances%20where%20an%20estimated%20180%20women%20are%20giving%20birth%20in%20Gaza%20each%20day.%20Of%20these%20180%20women%2C%20the%20WHO%20warns%20that%2015%20per%20cent%20are%20likely%20to%20experience%20pregnancy%20or%20birth-related%20complications%20and%20need%20additional%20medical%20care.%20That%20care%20is%20simply%20not%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPattern%20of%20conduct%20indicates%20intent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sum%2C%20Madam%20President%2C%20all%20of%20these%20acts%2C%20individually%20and%20collectively%2C%20form%20a%20calculated%20pattern%20of%20conduct%20by%20Israel%2C%20indicating%20a%20genocidal%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20intent%20is%20evident%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(1)%20specially%20targeting%20Palestinians%20living%20in%20Gaza%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(2)%20using%20weaponry%20that%20causes%20large-scale%20homicidal%20destruction%2C%20as%20well%20as%20targeted%20sniping%20of%20civilians%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(3)%20designating%20safe%20zones%20for%20Palestinians%20to%20seek%20refuge%20and%20then%20bombing%20these%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(4)%20depriving%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20of%20basic%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20food%2C%20water%2C%20healthcare%2C%20fuel%2C%20sanitation%20and%20communications%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(5)%20destroying%20social%20infrastructure%3A%20homes%2C%20schools%2C%20mosques%2C%20churches%2C%20hospitals%3B%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(6)%20killing%2C%20seriously%20injuring%20and%20leaving%20large%20numbers%20of%20children%20orphaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenocides%20are%20never%20declared%20in%20advance.%20But%20this%20Court%20has%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20past%2013%20weeks%20of%20evidence%20that%20shows%20incontrovertibly%20a%20pattern%20of%20conduct%20and%20related%20intention%20that%20justifies%20a%20plausible%20claim%20of%20genocidal%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20The%20Gambia%20v.%20Myanmar%20case%2C%20this%20Court%20did%20not%20hesitate%20to%20impose%20provisional%20measures%20in%20relation%20to%20allegations%20that%20Myanmar%20was%20committing%20genocidal%20acts%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20within%20the%20Rakhine%20State.%20The%20facts%20before%20the%20Court%20today%20are%2C%20sadly%2C%20even%20more%20stark%2C%20and%20like%20The%20Gambia%20v.%20Myanmar%20case%2C%20deserve%20and%20demand%20this%20Court%E2%80%99s%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20there%20is%20mounting%20irreparable%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20property%2C%20dignity%20and%20humanity%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Our%20newsfeeds%20show%20graphic%20images%20of%20suffering%20that%20has%20become%20unbearable%20to%20watch.%20Nothing%20will%20stop%20this%20suffering%2C%20except%20an%20order%20from%20this%20Court.%20Without%20an%20indication%20of%20provisional%20measures%2C%20the%20atrocities%20will%20continue%3B%20with%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20indicating%20that%20they%20intend%20pursuing%20this%20course%20of%20action%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Under-Secretary%20General%20on%205%20January%202024%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20think%20getting%20aid%20into%20Gaza%20is%20easy%3F%20Think%20again.%20Three%20layers%20of%20inspections%20before%20trucks%20can%20even%20enter.%20Confusion%20and%20long%20queues.%20A%20growing%20list%20of%20rejected%20items.%20A%20crossing%20point%20meant%20for%20pedestrians%2C%20not%20trucks.%20Another%20crossing%20point%20where%20trucks%20have%20been%20blocked%20by%20desperate%2C%20hungry%20communities.%20A%20destroyed%20commercial%20sector.%20Constant%20bombardments.%20Poor%20communications.%20Damaged%20roads.%20Convoys%20shot%20at.%20Delays%20at%20checkpoints.%20A%20traumatized%20and%20exhausted%20population%20crammed%20into%20a%20smaller%20and%20smaller%20sliver%20of%20land.%20Shelters%20which%20have%20long%20exceeded%20their%20full%20capacity.%20Aid%20workers%20themselves%20displaced%2C%20killed.%20This%20is%20an%20impossible%20situation%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20for%20those%20trying%20to%20help%20them.%20The%20fighting%20must%20stop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadam%20President%2C%20Members%20of%20the%20Court%2C%20that%20concludes%20my%20section%20on%20the%20genocidal%20conduct%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20thank%20you%20for%20your%20patient%20attention%2C%20and%20I%20ask%20that%20you%20call%20Advocate%20Ngcukaitobi%20to%20the%20podium%20to%20address%20the%20Court%20on%20genocidal%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAdila%20Hassim%20is%20one%20of%20the%20South%20African%20lawyers%20fighting%20the%20case%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20genocide%20at%20the%20ICJ.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705052201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12150511%2FScreenshot-2024-01-12-at-3.04.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-south-africa-genocidal-acts-icj%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Israel%20is%20blocking%20the%20delivery%20of%20life-saving%20aid%2C%20including%20essential%20medical%20kits%20for%20delivering%20babies%2C%20in%20circumstances%20where%20an%20estimated%20180%20women%20are%20giving%20birth%20in%20Gaza%20each%20day.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-south-africa-genocidal-acts-icj%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%