ns%2C%20forcing%20to%20move%20the%20venue%20around%2034%20km%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-to-begin-from-private-ground-in-manipurs-thoubal%2Farticleshow%2F106759255.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20conducts%20flight-test%20of%20new-generation%20AKASH%20missile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705048266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106759188%2Cimgsize-1248749.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-successfully-conducts-flight-test-of-new-generation-akash-missile%2Farticleshow%2F106758659.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20successfully%20conducted%20a%20flight%20test%20of%20the%20new%20generation%20AKASH%20missile%20at%20the%20Integrated%20Test%20Range%20in%20Chandipur%2C%20Odisha.%20The%20missile%20intercepted%20and%20destroyed%20a%20high-speed%20unmanned%20aerial%20target%20flying%20at%20a%20very%20low%20altitude.%20The%20test%20validated%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20entire%20weapon%20system%2C%20including%20the%20indigenously%20developed%20Radio%20Frequency%20Seeker%2C%20Launcher%2C%20Multi-Function%20Radar%2C%20and%20Command%2C%20Control%20%26amp%3B%20Communication%20system.%20The%20AKASH-NG%20system%20is%20capable%20of%20intercepting%20high-speed%2C%20agile%20aerial%20threats%2C%20and%20the%20successful%20test%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20user%20trials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-successfully-conducts-flight-test-of-new-generation-akash-missile%2Farticleshow%2F106758659.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Political%20Propaganda'%3A%20UGC%20Directive%20to%20Universities%20to%20Use%20'Beti%20Bachao'%20Logo%20Draws%20Flak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%E2%80%99s%20directive%20to%20universities%20and%20colleges%20in%20the%20country%20to%20install%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%20(BBBP)%20logo%20on%20their%20premises%20has%20drawn%20flak%20from%20academics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fpropaganda-cry-as-university-grants-commission-asks-varsities-to-use-beti-bachao-logo%2Fcid%2F1993149%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20say%20such%20moves%20are%20aimed%20at%20advancing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20propaganda%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinterfere%20with%20the%20autonomy%20of%20educational%20institutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20request%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20women%20and%20child%20development%2C%20which%20is%20the%20nodal%20ministry%20for%20the%20BBBP%20campaign%2C%20UGC%20has%20written%20to%20vice-chancellors%20of%20universities%20and%20principals%20of%20all%20colleges%20to%20use%20the%20BBBP%20logos%20to%20create%20awareness%20on%20valuing%20the%20girl%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20regard%2C%20MWCD%20proposed%20to%20create%20awareness%20on%20the%20valuing%20of%20the%20girl%20child%20and%20also%20enclosed%20the%20logo%20and%20tagline%20of%20BBBP.%20The%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20are%20requested%20to%20use%20BBBP%20logo%20on%20the%20website%2C%20portals%2C%20stationery%20items%2C%20events%20and%20prominent%20places%20in%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20HEIs.%20It%20will%20convey%20the%20commitment%20of%20ensuring%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20girl%20child%20and%20empowerment%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20UGC%20letter%20to%20universities%20and%20colleges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20higher%20education%20regulatory%20authority%20has%20also%20asked%20institutions%20to%20upload%20details%20of%20the%20activities%20they%20conduct%2C%20with%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20on%20the%20University%20Activity%20Monitoring%20Portal%20(https%3A%2F%2Fuamo.uec.ac.in%2F).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20John%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20academic%20council%20of%20Delhi%20University%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20UGC%20letter%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdiktat%20for%20creating%20political%20propaganda%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%20She%20said%20such%20moves%20distract%20universities%20and%20educational%20institutions%20from%20%E2%80%9Ccritical%20areas%20like%20teaching%20and%20research%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20become%20a%20pattern%20that%20the%20government%20and%20the%20UGC%20are%20regularly%20nudging%20the%20educational%20institutions%20to%20conduct%20activities%20like%20awareness%20on%20G20%20and%20the%20Swachhata%20campaign.%20These%20are%20purely%20political%20propaganda%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20academic%20who%20chose%20not%20to%20be%20named%20said%20that%20the%20UGC%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdeviating%E2%80%9D%20from%20its%20mandate%20of%20maintaining%20academic%20standards.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UGC%20is%20deviating%20from%20its%20core%20mandate%20and%20doing%20things%20beyond%20its%20domain.%20The%20way%20vice-chancellors%20are%20being%20appointed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20ideology%20and%20other%20non-academic%20considerations%2C%20they%20do%20not%20oppose%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20diktats%20passed%20through%20the%20UGC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20a%20state%20university%20concurred%20with%20the%20views.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UGC%20is%20doing%20this%20deliberately.%20This%20should%20be%20challenged%20in%20court%20to%20stop%20the%20UGC%20and%20the%20government%20from%20interfering%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20educational%20institutions%20over%20non-academic%20activities.%20The%20UGC%20should%20rather%20suggest%20how%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20education%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20decline%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20latest%20directive%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20another%20circular%20where%20higher%20education%20institutions%20were%20asked%20to%20set%20up%20selfie%20points%20with%20cutouts%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20which%20also%20came%20under%20severe%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705048224000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpolitical-propaganda-ugc-directive-to-universities-to-use-beti-bachao-logo-draws-flak%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20directed%20higher%20education%20institutions%20in%20the%20country%20to%20use%20Beti%20Bachao%20Beti%20Padhao%20logo%20on%20their%20website%2C%20portals%2C%20stationery%20items%2C%20events%2C%20and%20prominent%20places%20in%20their%20premises.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpolitical-propaganda-ugc-directive-to-universities-to-use-beti-bachao-logo-draws-flak%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20strikes%20may%20be%20counterproductive%20and%20dangerous%20-%20and%20could%20lead%20to%20unanticipated%20attacks%20elsewhere%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705047900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-yemen-raf-typhoon_6418907.jpg%3F20240112070523%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fstrikes-against-houthi