zes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12123156%2FNajma.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12123156%2FNajma.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12123156%2FNajma-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12123156%2FNajma-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692535%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENajma%20Baloch%2C%20holding%20her%20brother%20Balach%20Mola%20Baksh%E2%80%99s%20picture.%20Photo%3A%20Veengas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20state%20has%20a%20%E2%80%98genocide%20policy%E2%80%99%20against%20Balochs%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Pakistan%2C%20some%20raised%20objections%20to%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98Baloch%20genocide%E2%80%99%20used%20in%20the%20protest.%20Mahrang%20criticised%20them%20and%20asked%20if%20they%20felt%20uncomfortable%20by%20Balochs%20who%20were%20highlighting%20the%20truth.%20She%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20Balochs%20not%20use%20the%20term%20when%20their%20sixth%20generation%20is%20being%20killed.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20employing%20a%20genocide%20policy%20against%20Balochs%20for%20decades.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20word%20%E2%80%98genocide%E2%80%99%20hurts%20them%20because%20it%20reveals%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cmark%3EMahrang%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20mass%20graves%20have%20been%20found%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20questioned%20why%20they%20should%20remain%20silent%20as%20the%20grave%20on%20the%20graveyard%20named%20Edhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBalochs%20are%20in%20a%20queue%20at%20the%20hospital%20when%20they%20receive%20news%20about%20a%20missing%20person%20found%20dead.%20Our%20people%20are%20finding%20their%20relatives%20in%20shrouds.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20ever%20feel%20the%20pain%20of%20those%20families%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20state%20has%20every%20intention%20of%20erasing%20Baloch%20identity.%20The%20state%20identifies%20Balochs%20to%20kill%20and%20abduct%20them.%20Even%20if%20someone%20moves%20to%20another%20country%2C%20say%20Dubai%2C%20the%20state%20abducts%20them%20from%20there%20just%20because%20they%20are%20Baloch.%20Moreover%2C%20Baloch%20students%20are%20targeted%20and%20profiled.%20The%20students%20cannot%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20because%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20threats.%20Even%20Balochs%20who%20live%20in%20D.G.%20Khan%2C%20which%20was%20illegally%20annexed%20with%20Punjab%2C%20face%20abductions%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20state%20uses%20every%20cruel%20act%20to%20kill%20Balochs.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20against%20Balochs%2C%20we%20will%20call%20it%20Baloch%20genocide%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mahrang.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%20that%20all%20their%20demands%20are%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20constitution.%20If%20a%20UN%20inquiry%20could%20be%20formed%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20late%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20why%20not%20in%20their%20case%3F%20She%20does%20not%20understand%20why%20the%20state%20is%20afraid%20of%20accepting%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20UN%20inquiry%20when%20it%20claims%20that%20the%20state%20is%20not%20committing%20crimes.%20If%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20let%20the%20UN%20invite%20them%20to%20see%20the%20truth%20and%20determine%20who%20is%20responsible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20responded%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20denial%20of%20the%20alleged%20death%20squad%20and%20said%20she%20did%20not%20need%20to%20convince%20the%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20squads%20exist%20and%20are%20fully%20supported%20by%20the%20state.%20Balochistan%20has%20mass%20graves%20because%20of%20death%20squads%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMurtaza%20Solangi%2C%20federal%20caretaker%20minister%20for%20information%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20our%20messages%20for%20a%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20counter-protest%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20group%20of%20people%20have%20set%20up%20a%20counter-protest%20against%20the%20Baloch%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest.%20Pictures%20of%20those%20leading%20the%20counter-protest%20were%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20Some%20have%20claimed%20that%20this%20group%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20death%20squads.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20state%20has%20supported%20a%20counter-protest%20to%20weaken%20the%20Baloch%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest%2C%20posing%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20entered%20Islamabad%2C%20we%20were%20baton-charged%20and%20jailed%2C%20but%20this%20group%20has%20been%20welcomed%20and%20even%20facilitated.%20It%20clearly%20shows%20which%20side%20the%20state%20is%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mahrang.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705046809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12122526%2FBaloch-Missing-Persons-Title.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbaloch-women-continue-protest-despite-police-action-government-indifference%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20government%20tells%20us%20where%20our%20relatives%20are%2C%20then%2C%20we%20will%20leave%20your%20Islamabad%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20protestor%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbaloch-women-continue-protest-despite-police-action-government-indifference%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%