u-ceo-goa-child-murder-how-an-accident-on-goa-border-led-police-to-ceo-who-killed-her-child-4837044%5C%22%3Ekilled%20her%20four-year-old%20son%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20apartment.%20She%20then%20allegedly%20stuffed%20the%20body%20in%20a%20bag%20and%20took%20it%20to%20Karnataka%20in%20a%20taxi%20on%20Monday%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20child%20was%20smothered%20to%20death%20either%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%20or%20a%20pillow%2C%20the%20post-mortem%20revealed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20was%20arrested%20from%20Karnataka%20on%20Monday%20night%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20cab%20driver.%20The%20driver%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoa-child-murder-case-cab-driver-who-helped-cops-catch-murder-accused-ceo-says-suchana-seth-was-calm-4847354%5C%22%3ESeth%20did%20not%20utter%20a%20single%20word%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20entire%20trip%20which%20lasted%20more%20than%2010%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPolice%20sources%20say%20that%20she%20has%20not%20been%20cooperating%20with%20the%20investigation%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuchana-seth-news-goa-child-murder-suchana-seth-seems-cool-shows-no-remorse-cops-on-bengaluru-ceo-murder-accused-4836114%5C%22%3Ehas%20shown%20%26quot%3Bno%20remorse%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20far%2C%20either%20over%20the%20death%20of%20her%20child%2C%20or%20her%20role%20in%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2039-year-old%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20bitter%20custody%20battle%20with%20her%20husband%20Venkat%20Raman.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-ceo-suchana-seth-murder-cops-find-note-on-mental-exhaustion-written-by-ceo-accused-of-killing-son-4846887%5C%22%3Ehandwritten%20note%20has%20been%20recovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20her%20belongings%20which%20she%20had%20written%20about%20her%20feud%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20the%20mental%20exhaustion%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20court%20p