gement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Feasemytrip-hits-a-patriotic-high-easy-trip-planners-shares-surge-amidst-india-maldives-row-but-should-you-buy%2Farticleshow%2F106754159.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20US-Led%20Strikes%20On%20Houthi%20Targets%20In%20Yemen%20Will%20Mean%20For%20Oil%20Prices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20launched%20airstrikes%20on%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20Houthi%20targets%20in%20Yemen%2C%20in%20retaliation%20for%20a%20spate%20of%20attacks%20on%20merchant%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20represents%20a%20major%20escalation%20of%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20that%20have%20been%20simmering%20since%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20in%20early%20October.%20Brent%20jumped%20as%20much%20as%202.5%25%20on%20fears%20there%20would%20be%20more%20disruption%20to%20shipping%2C%20and%20that%20the%20conflict%20could%20expand%20into%20a%20broader%20regional%20conflagration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Houthis%20vowing%20continued%20attacks%20on%20shipping%20and%20Iran%20condemning%20the%20action%2C%20here's%20what%20analysts%20are%20saying%20the%20heightened%20geopolitical%20risks%20mean%20for%20oil%20markets%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUBS%20Group%20AG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil's%20bounce%20was%20driven%20by%20the%20market's%20perception%20that%20this%20is%20an%20escalation%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20said%20Giovanni%20Staunovo%2C%20a%20commodity%20strategist%20at%20UBS%20Group%20AG.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bany%20risk%20premium%20will%20only%20sustain%20if%20there%20are%20disruptions%20to%20oil%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20look%20for%20higher%20prices%20over%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20expecting%20Brent%20to%20move%20above%20%2480%20a%20barrel%2C%20as%20result%20of%20OPEC%2B%20production%20cuts%20keeping%20the%20oil%20market%20slightly%20undersupplied%2C%26quot%3B%20Staunovo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EING%20Groep%20NV%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20UK%20airstrikes%20didn't%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%2C%20but%20given%20the%20threat%20faced%20by%20vessels%20and%20the%20disruptions%20to%20trade%20flows%20from%20Houthi%20attacks%2C%20it's%20clearly%20a%20ratcheting%20up%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20according%20to%20Warren%20Patterson%2C%20head%20of%20commodities%20strategy%20at%20ING%20Groep%20NV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20suggests%20%26quot%3Bgreater%20potential%20for%20disruptions%20and%20the%20need%20for%20vessels%20to%20divert%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20will%20provide%20upside%20to%20oil%20prices%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20bigger%20risk%20is%20if%20the%20conflict%20spreads%20and%20the%20market%20starts%20seeing%20threats%20to%20flows%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20believe%20the%20risk%20of%20this%20is%20low%2C%20the%20impact%20would%20be%20significant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanda%20Insights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuite%20a%20bit%20of%20the%20new%20risk%20premium%20has%20already%20been%20priced%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vandana%20Hari%2C%20founder%20of%20consultancy%20Vanda%20Insights.%20%26quot%3BWe%20might%20see%20crude%20stacking%20on%20another%20dollar%20or%20two...%20I%20expect%20a%20degree%20of%20restraint%20and%20back-channel%20diplomacy%20to%20keep%20the%20tensions%20from%20spiraling%20out%20of%20control%20and%20causing%20a%20regional%20conflagration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20as%20none%20of%20the%20powers%20involved%20want%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20to%20play%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fluctuations%20in%20prices%20will%20absolutely%20remain%20in%20place%20as%20the%20situation%20develops.%20It's%20an%20uneven%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20a%20bearish%20outlook%20on%20fundamentals%20and%20a%20supportive%20Mideast%20risk%20premium%2C%26quot%3B%20Hari%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%20now%2C%20both%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20remain%20in%20play%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWestpac%20Banking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%2C%20UK%20had%20warned%20that%20action%20would%20take%20place%20if%20the%20Houthi%20rebels%20continued%20their%20attacks%2C%20so%20this%20action%20should%20not%20really%20be%20unexpected%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robert%20Rennie%2C%20head%20of%20commodity%20and%20carbon%20research%20at%20Westpac%20Banking%20Corp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarkets%20have%20arguably%20been%20too%20focused%20on%20rising%20global%20supply%20through%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20while%20the%20sharp%20deterioration%20in%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20has%20been%20underplayed%20so%20far%20in%202024%2C%20he%20said.%20Given%20that%20Houthi%20leaders%20have%20said%20any%20US%20attack%20would%20not%20go%20without%20a%20response%2C%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20could%20rise%20above%20%2475%20a%20barrel%20and%20Brent%20could%20surpass%20%2480.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaxo%20Capital%20Markets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airstrikes%20have%20raised%20the%20risk%20of%20an%20escalation%20and%20that%20could%20bring%20oil%20and%20haven%20demand%20in%20focus%20in%20the%20very%20near%20term%2C%20said%20Charu%20Chanana%2C%20market%20strategist%20for%20Saxo%20Capital%20Markets%20Pte.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20upside%20risks%20to%20oil%20prices%20if%20the%20conflict%20escalates%2C%20and%20volatility%20could%20increase%20%26quot%3Bas%20oil%20markets%20continue%20to%20assess%20the%20several%20catalysts%20from%20OPEC%2B%20cuts%20to%20non-OPEC%20supply%20and%20the%20US%20and%20China%20demand%20outlook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%