the%20international%20great%20power%20hierarchy%2C%20it%20envisions%20to%20project%20itself%20as%20a%20leading%20and%20responsible%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Don%20McLain%20Gill%20of%20De%20La%20Salle%20University%20in%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20naval%20deployment%20is%20part%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bdesire%20to%20play%20a%20larger%20and%20more%20proactive%20role%20as%20a%20responsible%20security%20and%20development%20partner%26quot%3B%2C%20Gill%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'Very%20proactive%20action'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20combat%20operations%20against%20pirates%20are%20not%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20navy%20has%20been%20deployed%20continuously%20off%20Somalia%20since%202008%20as%20piracy%20surged%2C%20bombarding%20and%20sinking%20pirate%20%26quot%3Bmotherships%26quot%3B%20ranging%20from%20just%20off%20India's%20coast%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%20boarding%20boats%20by%20helicopter%20and%20capturing%20dozens%20of%20gunmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20navy's%20deployment%20in%20December%20of%20a%20far%20larger%20force%20--%20including%20three%20guided-missile%20destroyers%20and%20P-8I%20reconnaissance%20aircraft%20to%20%26quot%3Bmaintain%20a%20deterrent%20presence%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20string%20of%20shipping%20attacks%20--%20marks%20a%20rapid%20ramping%20up%20of%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20--%20speaking%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20India's%20latest%20own-built%20warship%2C%20joining%20an%20indigenous-made%20fleet%20including%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20submarines%20--%20vowed%20shipping%20would%20be%20protected%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20the%20sea%20to%20the%20heights%20of%20the%20sky%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20followed%20a%20December%2023%20drone%20attack%20on%20the%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%20tanker%20370%20kilometres%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20India%2C%20which%20Washington%20blamed%20on%20Iran%20--%20claims%20Tehran%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bworthless%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYemen's%20Iran-backed%20Houthis%20have%20launched%20scores%20of%20Red%20Sea%20attacks%20targeting%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20response%20to%20Israel's%20war%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%2C%20which%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20which%20has%20close%20trade%20ties%20with%20Iran%2C%20has%20not%20joined%20the%20US-led%20force%20battling%20the%20Houthis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20US%20and%20British%20forces%20had%20launched%20air%20strikes%20against%20Huthi%20targets%20in%20Yemen%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdefensive%20action%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20vessels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20nine%20allies%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20that%20their%20aim%20was%20to%20stabilise%20the%20crucial%20shipping%20lanes%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20the%20free%20flow%20of%20commerce%26quot%3B%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20international%20naval%20forces%20diverted%20north%20into%20the%20Red%20Sea%20--%20sparking%20fears%20of%20resurgent%20pirates%20exploiting%20the%20gap%2C%20with%20the%20first%20successful%20case%20of%20Somali%20piracy%20since%202017%20recorded%20in%20December%20--%20New%20Delhi%20remains%20worried%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20report%2C%20by%20New%20Delhi-based%20Research%20and%20Information%20System%20for%20Developing%20Countries%2C%20warned%20India%20could%20lose%20%2430%20billion%20in%20exports%20this%20year%20--%20a%20six%20percent%20drop%20--%20if%20more%20shipping%20has%20to%20reroute%20via%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Centre%20was%20taking%20%26quot%3Bvery%20proactive%20action%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20pirates%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20venture%20out%20into%20the%20India%20Ocean%20region%26quot%3B%2C%20Admiral%20Hari%20Kumar%2C%20chief%20of%20naval%20staff%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E'Run%20away%20like%20rats'%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%205%2C%20after%20the%20Liberian-flagged%20MV%20Lila%20Norfolk%20reported%20an%20attempted%20hijacking%20around%20450%20nautical%20miles%20off%20Somalia's%20coast%2C%20an%20Indian%20destroyer%20and%20surveillance%20aircraft%20tracked%20the%20vessel%20giving%20a%20%26quot%3Bforceful%20warning%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20showed%20India%20%26quot%3Bcan%20mount%20a%20credible%20naval%20presence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%20when%20required%20at%20short%20notice%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Bhaskar%2C%20who%20is%20a%20retired%20naval%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20and%20New%20Delhi%20are%20vying%20for%20influence%20across%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20and%20India%20has%20previously%20deployed%20patrols%20to%20the%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea%20and%20Western%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20expanded%20its%20force%20into%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20at%20a%20time%20when%20rival%20Asian%20power%20China%20has%20been%20more%20%26quot%3Bcautious%20in%20its%20response%20given%20its%20worry%20of%20not%20upsetting%20its%20recently%20developing%20ties%20with%20the%20Arab%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20Gill%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20navy%20spokesman%20DK%20Sharma%20insisted%20the%20deployment%20was%20targeted%20only%20at%20%26quot%3Bmiscreants%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%26quot%3B%20by%20attacking%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20believes%20in%20maintaining%20peace%20in%20the%20global%20commons%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20ambitions%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20India's%20ocean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20also%20confident%20Beijing%20had%20%26quot%3Btaken%20note%26quot%3B%20of%20India's%20rapid%20response%20forcing%20pirates%20to%20%26quot%3Brun%20away%20like%20rats%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20can%20view%20it%20the%20way%20they