02020%20and%20a%20full%20resolution%20of%20the%20border%20crisis%20through%20ongoing%20negotiations%20still%20appears%20distant.%20So%20far%2C%20there%20have%20been%20four%20rounds%20of%20disengagement%20from%20Galwan%20Valley%2C%20Pangong%20Tso%2C%20Gogra%20(PP-17A)%2C%20and%20Hot%20Springs%20(PP-15)%2C%20yet%20there%20are%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops%20each%20and%20advanced%20weaponry%20deployed%20in%20the%20Ladakh%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Army%20chief%20said%20India%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclosely%20monitoring%E2%80%9D%20the%20situation%20as%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20are%20currently%20engaged%20in%20resolving%20their%20longstanding%20boundary%20dispute.%20%E2%80%9CBhutan%20and%20we%20(India)%20share%20mutual%20security%20concerns%20which%20both%20of%20us%20are%20aware%20of.%20The%20ongoing%20talks%20on%20the%20boundary%20which%20you%20alluded%20to%2C%20we%20are%20closely%20monitoring.%20We%20are%20interacting%20with%20our%20friends%20in%20Bhutan%20on%20a%20transparent%20and%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fclosely-monitoring-army-chief-gen-pande-on-bhutan-china-boundary-talks-124011100797_1.html%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20termed%20the%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20Bhutan%20as%20one%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cutmost%20trust%2C%20goodwill%2C%20and%20mutual%20understanding%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20relationship%20also%20transcends%20into%20the%20military%20domain%20as%20we%20have%20IMTRAT%20(Indian%20Military%20Training%20Team)%20right%20from%20the%20early%201960s.%20They%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%E2%80%9D%20General%20Pande%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20making%20progress%20on%20their%20boundary%20talks%2C%20there%20is%20a%20talk%20of%20possible%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%5C%22%3Esecurity%20implications%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20chief%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20resurgence%20of%20terror%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20four%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%20in%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20area.%20He%20said%20the%20Army%20has%20sent%20more%20troops%20to%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20sector%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20resurgence%20of%20terror%20in%20the%20sensitive%20area%2C%20while%20reorienting%20its%20units%20operating%20in%20the%20area.%20He%20said%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20strengthen%20the%20intelligence%20network%20for%20conducting%20counterterror%20operations%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20get%20into%20what%20has%20gone%20wrong%2C%20rather%20I%20will%20say%20what%20it%20is%20that%20we%20are%20doing.%20We%20have%20increased%20our%20deployment%20in%20those%20areas%20and%20reorientated%20some%20of%20the%20units.%20We%20are%20strengthening%20our%20human%20intelligence%20network%20as%20well%20as%20technical%20intelligence.%20That%20is%20something%20we%20are%20working%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerror%20returned%20to%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20sector%20on%20December%2021%20last%20year%20when%20four%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%20%E2%80%93%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20that%20have%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20several%20army%20personnel%20during%20the%20last%20year.%20In%202023%2C%2071%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20including%2051%20in%20the%20Valley%20and%2020%20in%20the%20Rajouri-Poonch%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705035471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F30163752%2FScreenshot-2023-03-30-at-4.37.44-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsituation-on-lac-stable-but-sensitive-closely-monitoring-bhutan-chi