is%20Jay%E2%80%99s%20friend%2C%20was%20working%20as%20a%20network%20engineer%20in%20a%20good%20company%20until%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20YouTube%20was%20a%20relatively%20new%20platform%20for%20rural%20areas%20like%20theirs.%20They%20decided%20to%20explore%20it%20as%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20require%20a%20significant%20investment.%20While%20Jay%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20originality%20and%20started%20handling%20creative%20aspects%2C%20Gyanendra%20focused%20on%20the%20technical%20side%20of%20the%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20technical%20knowledge%20comes%20naturally%20to%20me%2C%20so%20as%20a%20side%20hustle%20and%20out%20of%20passion%2C%20we%20began%20making%20videos%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gyanendra.%20They%20made%20videos%20with%20the%20children%20from%20their%20village%20and%20eventually%20formed%20a%20team%2C%20creating%20several%20channels.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYouTube%20would%20sometimes%20delete%20our%20channels%20because%20we%20maybe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20comply%20with%20their%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20duo%20says.%20Due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20about%20the%20platform%2C%20they%20learned%20through%20trial%20and%20error.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2014%20January%2C%202018%2C%20they%20launched%20the%20YouTube%20channel%20%E2%80%98Being%20Chhattisgarhiya%E2%80%99.%20As%20they%20continued%2C%20people%20began%20to%20notice%20their%20work%2C%20which%20was%20not%20typically%20considered%20as%20a%20regular%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20YouTubers%20of%20Tulsi%20village%2C%20Raipur.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FYoutubers-at-Tulsi-Village-Raipur_11zon-1704460010-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337622%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20YouTubers%20of%20Tulsi%20village%2C%20Raipur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInitial%20hiccups%20and%20successes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Jay%20and%20Gyanendra%E2%80%99s%20families%20have%20still%20not%20completely%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20their%20YouTube%20careers.%20They%20do%20not%20look%20at%20what%20they%20do%20as%20something%20which%20will%20give%20them%20security.%20Initially%2C%20both%20of%20them%20were%20criticised%20a%20lot%20by%20their%20family%20members%20to%20have%20left%20%E2%80%98better%E2%80%99%20jobs%20for%20YouTube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20gained%202-3%20thousand%20subscribers%20within%20a%20month.%20Our%20videos%20were%20circulating%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20which%20was%20a%20significant%20help.%20We%20used%20to%20create%20short%20videos%2C%20often%20without%20much%20understanding%2C%20preparation%2C%20or%20ideas.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%201%2C20%2C000%20subscribers%20on%20our%20channel%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Gyanendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20wish%20was%20to%20make%20movies.%20Our%20goal%20was%20to%20do%20something%20that%20could%20provide%20employment%20to%20all%20the%20villages.%20We%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20a